WEBVTT

00:00:39.039 --> 00:00:43.636
<b><font color="#ffff00"><i>Long before the birth
of light, there was darkness.</i></font></b>

00:00:43.794 --> 00:00:47.844
<b><font color="#ffff00"><i>And from that darkness
came the Dark Elves.</i></font></b>

00:00:49.716 --> 00:00:53.437
<b><font color="#ffff00"><i>Millennia ago, the most
ruthless of their kind, Malekith</i></font></b>

00:00:53.595 --> 00:00:58.442
<b><font color="#ffff00"><i>sought to transform our universe
back into one of eternal night.</i></font></b>

00:01:00.894 --> 00:01:05.616
<b><font color="#ffff00"><i>Such evil was possible through
the power of the Aether,</i></font></b>

00:01:05.816 --> 00:01:09.491
<b><font color="#ffff00"><i>an ancient force of
infinite destruction.</i></font></b>

00:01:12.656 --> 00:01:13.782
<b><font color="#ffff00">Malekith.</font></b>

00:01:13.949 --> 00:01:15.667
<b><font color="#ffff00">Asgard's forces are upon us.</font></b>

00:01:24.084 --> 00:01:28.385
<b><font color="#ffff00">The noble armies of Asgard,
led by my father, King Bor,</font></b>

00:01:28.505 --> 00:01:31.429
<b><font color="#ffff00">waged a mighty war
against these creatures.</font></b>

00:01:42.394 --> 00:01:44.692
<b><font color="#ffff00">Send in the Kursed!</font></b>

00:02:01.496 --> 00:02:04.295
<b><font color="#ffff00">As the Nine Worlds
converged above him,</font></b>

00:02:04.374 --> 00:02:08.845
<b><font color="#ffff00">Malekith could at last
unleash the Aether.</font></b>

00:02:23.060 --> 00:02:24.152
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ahh!</font></b>

00:02:26.980 --> 00:02:30.234
<b><font color="#ffff00">But Asgard ripped
the weapon from his grasp.</font></b>

00:02:31.276 --> 00:02:33.449
<b><font color="#ffff00">Without it, the Dark Elves fell.</font></b>

00:02:48.335 --> 00:02:49.928
<b><font color="#ffff00">With the battle all but lost,</font></b>

00:02:50.212 --> 00:02:52.590
<b><font color="#ffff00">Malekith sacrificed his own people</font></b>

00:02:53.423 --> 00:02:57.473
<b><font color="#ffff00">in a desperate attempt to lay
waste to Asgard's army.</font></b>

00:03:00.305 --> 00:03:02.649
<b><font color="#ffff00">Their deaths will
mean our survival.</font></b>

00:03:04.101 --> 00:03:06.103
<b><font color="#ffff00">This war is far from over.</font></b>

00:03:13.735 --> 00:03:19.333
<b><font color="#ffff00">Malekith was vanquished,
and the Aether was no more.</font></b>

00:03:20.367 --> 00:03:22.244
<b><font color="#ffff00">Or so we were led to believe.</font></b>

00:03:23.704 --> 00:03:27.049
<b><font color="#ffff00">Sire, the Aether.
Shall we destroy it?</font></b>

00:03:27.708 --> 00:03:30.086
<b><font color="#ffff00">If only we could.</font></b>

00:03:30.252 --> 00:03:32.095
<b><font color="#ffff00">But its power is too great.</font></b>

00:03:32.796 --> 00:03:35.174
<b><font color="#ffff00">Bury it deep.</font></b>

00:03:35.549 --> 00:03:37.722
<b><font color="#ffff00">Somewhere no one will ever find it.</font></b>

00:04:19.509 --> 00:04:20.556
<b><font color="#ffff00">Loki.</font></b>

00:04:21.052 --> 00:04:22.269
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hello, Mother.</font></b>

00:04:23.096 --> 00:04:24.643
<b><font color="#ffff00">Have I made you proud?</font></b>

00:04:24.806 --> 00:04:27.184
<b><font color="#ffff00">Please, don't make this worse.</font></b>

00:04:27.517 --> 00:04:29.110
<b><font color="#ffff00">Define "worse."</font></b>

00:04:29.269 --> 00:04:30.862
<b><font color="#ffff00">Enough!</font></b>

00:04:31.021 --> 00:04:33.319
<b><font color="#ffff00">I will speak to the prisoner alone.</font></b>

00:04:47.370 --> 00:04:49.714
<b><font color="#ffff00">I really don't see
what all the fuss is about.</font></b>

00:04:49.873 --> 00:04:53.252
<b><font color="#ffff00">Do you not truly feel
the gravity of your crimes?</font></b>

00:04:53.376 --> 00:04:56.220
<b><font color="#ffff00">Wherever you go, there is war, ruin,</font></b>

00:04:56.880 --> 00:04:58.382
<b><font color="#ffff00">and death.</font></b>

00:04:58.548 --> 00:05:02.769
<b><font color="#ffff00">I went down to Midgard to rule the
people of Earth as a benevolent god.</font></b>

00:05:03.637 --> 00:05:05.105
<b><font color="#ffff00">Just like you.</font></b>

00:05:05.430 --> 00:05:09.060
<b><font color="#ffff00">We are not gods.
We are born, we live, we die.</font></b>

00:05:09.434 --> 00:05:11.607
<b><font color="#ffff00">Just as humans do.</font></b>

00:05:12.562 --> 00:05:14.940
<b><font color="#ffff00">Give or take 5,000 years.</font></b>

00:05:15.106 --> 00:05:18.861
<b><font color="#ffff00">All this because Loki
desires a throne.</font></b>

00:05:19.027 --> 00:05:20.370
<b><font color="#ffff00">It is my birthright.</font></b>

00:05:20.529 --> 00:05:23.874
<b><font color="#ffff00">Your birthright was to die</font></b>

00:05:24.366 --> 00:05:25.913
<b><font color="#ffff00">as a child.</font></b>

00:05:27.035 --> 00:05:29.504
<b><font color="#ffff00">Cast out onto a frozen rock.</font></b>

00:05:31.414 --> 00:05:33.633
<b><font color="#ffff00">If I had not taken you in,</font></b>

00:05:33.792 --> 00:05:36.420
<b><font color="#ffff00">you would not be
here now to hate me.</font></b>

00:05:36.628 --> 00:05:38.722
<b><font color="#ffff00">If I am for the axe,
then for mercy's sake,</font></b>

00:05:38.797 --> 00:05:41.300
<b><font color="#ffff00">just swing it.</font></b>

00:05:41.842 --> 00:05:43.562
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's not that I don't
love our little talks,</font></b>

00:05:43.677 --> 00:05:45.600
<b><font color="#ffff00">it's just...</font></b>

00:05:46.680 --> 00:05:48.353
<b><font color="#ffff00">I don't love them.</font></b>

00:05:48.515 --> 00:05:50.688
<b><font color="#ffff00">Frigga is the only reason
you're still alive,</font></b>

00:05:50.767 --> 00:05:52.189
<b><font color="#ffff00">and you will never see her again.</font></b>

00:05:53.103 --> 00:05:57.404
<b><font color="#ffff00">You will spend the rest of
your days in the dungeons.</font></b>

00:06:00.527 --> 00:06:02.655
<b><font color="#ffff00">And what of Thor?</font></b>

00:06:03.280 --> 00:06:06.875
<b><font color="#ffff00">You'll make that witless oaf
king while I rot in chains.</font></b>

00:06:07.033 --> 00:06:10.537
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thor must strive to undo
the damage you have done.</font></b>

00:06:10.704 --> 00:06:12.206
<b><font color="#ffff00">He will bring order
to the Nine Realms</font></b>

00:06:12.372 --> 00:06:14.340
<b><font color="#ffff00">and then, yes...</font></b>

00:06:15.250 --> 00:06:17.173
<b><font color="#ffff00">He will be king.</font></b>

00:06:26.887 --> 00:06:28.013
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ah!</font></b>

00:07:04.549 --> 00:07:06.267
<b><font color="#ffff00">I've got this completely
under control!</font></b>

00:07:06.426 --> 00:07:08.474
<b><font color="#ffff00">Is that why everything is on fire?</font></b>

00:07:23.443 --> 00:07:24.444
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ah!</font></b>

00:07:32.494 --> 00:07:34.041
<b><font color="#ffff00">You're welcome.</font></b>

00:07:36.706 --> 00:07:37.707
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ha!</font></b>

00:07:55.725 --> 00:07:56.772
<b><font color="#ffff00">All yours.</font></b>

00:08:19.374 --> 00:08:20.375
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hello.</font></b>

00:08:23.753 --> 00:08:25.300
<b><font color="#ffff00">I accept your surrender.</font></b>

00:08:38.184 --> 00:08:39.527
<b><font color="#ffff00">Anyone else?</font></b>

00:08:47.402 --> 00:08:50.952
<b><font color="#ffff00">Perhaps next time we should
start with the big one.</font></b>

00:08:51.990 --> 00:08:54.163
<b><font color="#ffff00">Keep moving. Come on!</font></b>

00:09:05.628 --> 00:09:08.097
<b><font color="#ffff00">Keep moving. Go ahead of me.
Don't you turn around!</font></b>

00:09:09.132 --> 00:09:10.884
<b><font color="#ffff00">Where do we go next?</font></b>

00:09:11.051 --> 00:09:15.022
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hogun, the peace is nearly won
across the Nine Realms.</font></b>

00:09:16.139 --> 00:09:18.688
<b><font color="#ffff00">You should stay here. Be with
your people, where your heart is.</font></b>

00:09:18.850 --> 00:09:20.443
<b><font color="#ffff00">Asgard can wait.</font></b>

00:09:21.853 --> 00:09:23.821
<b><font color="#ffff00">You have my thanks.</font></b>

00:09:24.606 --> 00:09:26.654
<b><font color="#ffff00">As you have mine.</font></b>

00:09:30.862 --> 00:09:32.455
<b><font color="#ffff00">Heimdall, when you're ready.</font></b>

00:10:17.450 --> 00:10:19.373
<b><font color="#ffff00">Is Vanaheim secure?</font></b>

00:10:19.536 --> 00:10:21.004
<b><font color="#ffff00">As are Nornheim and Ria.</font></b>

00:10:21.246 --> 00:10:23.846
<b><font color="#ffff00">Though our work would have gone
more quickly with you at the fore.</font></b>

00:10:24.582 --> 00:10:28.883
<b><font color="#ffff00">You must think I'm a piece of bread
that needs to be buttered so heavily.</font></b>

00:10:29.254 --> 00:10:31.131
<b><font color="#ffff00">That was not my intent.</font></b>

00:10:31.422 --> 00:10:33.641
<b><font color="#ffff00">For the first time
since Bifrost was destroyed,</font></b>

00:10:33.716 --> 00:10:35.514
<b><font color="#ffff00">the Nine Realms are at peace.</font></b>

00:10:35.677 --> 00:10:38.100
<b><font color="#ffff00">They're well reminded
of our strength</font></b>

00:10:38.263 --> 00:10:42.894
<b><font color="#ffff00">and you have earned their
respect and my gratitude.</font></b>

00:10:42.976 --> 00:10:44.102
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font></b>

00:10:44.978 --> 00:10:46.730
<b><font color="#ffff00">Nothing out of order</font></b>

00:10:46.980 --> 00:10:50.029
<b><font color="#ffff00">except your confused
and distracted heart.</font></b>

00:10:50.191 --> 00:10:52.444
<b><font color="#ffff00">This isn't about
Jane Foster, Father.</font></b>

00:10:52.861 --> 00:10:54.501
<b><font color="#ffff00">Human lives are fleeting,
they're nothing.</font></b>

00:10:54.654 --> 00:10:56.694
<b><font color="#ffff00">You'd be better served
by what lies in front of you.</font></b>

00:10:59.617 --> 00:11:01.039
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm telling you this,
not as the Allfather,</font></b>

00:11:01.119 --> 00:11:02.166
<b><font color="#ffff00">but as your father.</font></b>

00:11:02.245 --> 00:11:03.246
<b><font color="#ffff00">You are ready.</font></b>

00:11:03.580 --> 00:11:05.378
<b><font color="#ffff00">The time has come
for you to take the throne.</font></b>

00:11:05.498 --> 00:11:07.250
<b><font color="#ffff00">Embrace and celebrate
what you've won.</font></b>

00:11:07.834 --> 00:11:09.381
<b><font color="#ffff00">Join your warriors.</font></b>

00:11:09.460 --> 00:11:11.929
<b><font color="#ffff00">Eat and drink,
revel in their celebration.</font></b>

00:11:13.047 --> 00:11:15.391
<b><font color="#ffff00">At least pretend to enjoy yourself.</font></b>

00:12:00.220 --> 00:12:01.563
<b><font color="#ffff00">Another!</font></b>

00:12:17.862 --> 00:12:20.866
<b><font color="#ffff00">There was a time when you
would celebrate for weeks.</font></b>

00:12:22.200 --> 00:12:25.295
<b><font color="#ffff00">I remember you celebrated
the Battle of Harokin</font></b>

00:12:25.411 --> 00:12:27.664
<b><font color="#ffff00">so much that you nearly
started the second.</font></b>

00:12:28.331 --> 00:12:30.333
<b><font color="#ffff00">Well, the first was so much fun.</font></b>

00:12:36.798 --> 00:12:38.846
<b><font color="#ffff00">Take a drink with me.</font></b>

00:12:38.967 --> 00:12:42.016
<b><font color="#ffff00">Surely, the Allfather could have
no further task for you tonight.</font></b>

00:12:42.178 --> 00:12:44.021
<b><font color="#ffff00">No, this is one I set myself.</font></b>

00:12:45.765 --> 00:12:49.065
<b><font color="#ffff00">It does not go unnoticed that
you disappear each night.</font></b>

00:12:49.435 --> 00:12:51.437
<b><font color="#ffff00">There are nine realms.</font></b>

00:12:51.604 --> 00:12:54.574
<b><font color="#ffff00">The future king of Asgard
must focus on more than one.</font></b>

00:12:59.654 --> 00:13:01.406
<b><font color="#ffff00">I thank you for your sword</font></b>

00:13:01.489 --> 00:13:04.618
<b><font color="#ffff00">and for your counsel,
good Lady Sif.</font></b>

00:13:25.096 --> 00:13:26.097
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hi.</font></b>

00:13:26.931 --> 00:13:28.433
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hi.</font></b>

00:13:28.725 --> 00:13:29.925
<b><font color="#ffff00">So, what's the story with you?</font></b>

00:13:30.601 --> 00:13:32.641
<b><font color="#ffff00">Why does there have to be a story?
There's no story.</font></b>

00:13:32.729 --> 00:13:34.982
<b><font color="#ffff00">You spent the first
ten minutes of our date</font></b>

00:13:35.064 --> 00:13:37.032
<b><font color="#ffff00">hiding behind a menu
that has three choices on it.</font></b>

00:13:37.608 --> 00:13:39.531
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's either chicken,
vegetarian, or fish, Jane.</font></b>

00:13:39.902 --> 00:13:41.745
<b><font color="#ffff00">I think there's a story</font></b>

00:13:41.904 --> 00:13:45.078
<b><font color="#ffff00">and I'm thinking
the story involves a guy.</font></b>

00:13:45.742 --> 00:13:47.085
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's complicated.</font></b>

00:13:47.243 --> 00:13:48.415
<b><font color="#ffff00">Is he still around?</font></b>

00:13:48.619 --> 00:13:50.542
<b><font color="#ffff00">No, he...</font></b>

00:13:51.039 --> 00:13:52.211
<b><font color="#ffff00">Went away.</font></b>

00:13:52.373 --> 00:13:53.750
<b><font color="#ffff00">I've been there.</font></b>

00:13:53.916 --> 00:13:55.964
<b><font color="#ffff00">The going away.
It's hard, isn't it?</font></b>

00:13:56.252 --> 00:13:57.469
<b><font color="#ffff00">I was seeing a woman</font></b>

00:13:57.754 --> 00:13:59.427
<b><font color="#ffff00">and she took a job in New York.</font></b>

00:14:00.089 --> 00:14:01.887
<b><font color="#ffff00">Eventually, the distance killed it.</font></b>

00:14:02.091 --> 00:14:05.436
<b><font color="#ffff00">And the fact that she kept
sleeping with other dudes.</font></b>

00:14:05.595 --> 00:14:07.188
<b><font color="#ffff00">- No!
- Oh, so many.</font></b>

00:14:08.598 --> 00:14:11.351
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hi. Could we get some wine, please?</font></b>

00:14:11.517 --> 00:14:12.564
<b><font color="#ffff00">Sure, I'd love some.</font></b>

00:14:12.685 --> 00:14:14.278
<b><font color="#ffff00">Richard, this is Darcy.</font></b>

00:14:15.313 --> 00:14:16.781
<b><font color="#ffff00">What are you doing here?</font></b>

00:14:18.983 --> 00:14:19.984
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh. Hello.</font></b>

00:14:20.234 --> 00:14:23.829
<b><font color="#ffff00">So, I show up to work
at the lab/your mom's house,</font></b>

00:14:23.946 --> 00:14:27.667
<b><font color="#ffff00">fully expecting you to be
moping around in your pajamas,</font></b>

00:14:27.784 --> 00:14:29.502
<b><font color="#ffff00">eating ice cream and
obsessing about...</font></b>

00:14:29.660 --> 00:14:30.781
<b><font color="#ffff00">You know who.</font></b>

00:14:30.828 --> 00:14:31.875
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ah.</font></b>

00:14:31.996 --> 00:14:34.419
<b><font color="#ffff00">But you're not.
You're wearing lady clothes.</font></b>

00:14:34.540 --> 00:14:36.133
<b><font color="#ffff00">You even showered, didn't you?
You smell good.</font></b>

00:14:36.250 --> 00:14:37.251
<b><font color="#ffff00">Is there a point to all this?</font></b>

00:14:37.335 --> 00:14:39.415
<b><font color="#ffff00">Because there really needs
to be a point to all this.</font></b>

00:14:39.462 --> 00:14:40.679
<b><font color="#ffff00">Right.</font></b>

00:14:41.214 --> 00:14:43.774
<b><font color="#ffff00">You know all that scientific
equipment you don't look at anymore?</font></b>

00:14:44.300 --> 00:14:46.268
<b><font color="#ffff00">You might want
to start looking at it again.</font></b>

00:14:46.386 --> 00:14:48.434
<b><font color="#ffff00">This is the reason
we came all the way out here.</font></b>

00:14:48.554 --> 00:14:49.555
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's malfunctioning.</font></b>

00:14:49.639 --> 00:14:50.640
<b><font color="#ffff00">That's what I said.</font></b>

00:14:52.183 --> 00:14:53.605
<b><font color="#ffff00">That's what I did.</font></b>

00:14:53.684 --> 00:14:55.652
<b><font color="#ffff00">I thought you would do something
a little more scientific.</font></b>

00:14:55.812 --> 00:14:57.373
<b><font color="#ffff00">- I'm sure it's nothing.
- Yeah, it's...</font></b>

00:14:57.438 --> 00:14:58.610
<b><font color="#ffff00">It doesn't look like nothing.</font></b>

00:14:58.731 --> 00:15:01.251
<b><font color="#ffff00">It kind of looks like the readings
that Erik was rambling about.</font></b>

00:15:01.275 --> 00:15:02.367
<b><font color="#ffff00">Our friend Erik</font></b>

00:15:02.985 --> 00:15:04.487
<b><font color="#ffff00">kind of went banana balls.</font></b>

00:15:04.612 --> 00:15:05.579
<b><font color="#ffff00">He's not interested.</font></b>

00:15:05.655 --> 00:15:06.656
<b><font color="#ffff00">- I'm not interested.
- I'm interested.</font></b>

00:15:06.906 --> 00:15:08.328
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's time for you to go now.</font></b>

00:15:09.700 --> 00:15:10.792
<b><font color="#ffff00">Okay.</font></b>

00:15:13.996 --> 00:15:15.168
<b><font color="#ffff00">Short but sweet.</font></b>

00:15:15.248 --> 00:15:16.966
<b><font color="#ffff00">She needs help.</font></b>

00:15:20.336 --> 00:15:22.179
<b><font color="#ffff00">I think I'm going to
have the sea bass.</font></b>

00:15:22.338 --> 00:15:24.215
<b><font color="#ffff00">Sea bass, yeah.
Sea bass is good.</font></b>

00:15:25.258 --> 00:15:29.684
<b><font color="#ffff00">Sea bass, sea bass, sea bass,
sea bass, sea bass, sea bass.</font></b>

00:15:29.846 --> 00:15:32.315
<b><font color="#ffff00">Sea bass...</font></b>

00:15:33.599 --> 00:15:34.600
<b><font color="#ffff00">Sea bass.</font></b>

00:15:34.684 --> 00:15:36.106
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane?</font></b>

00:15:36.185 --> 00:15:37.778
<b><font color="#ffff00">Maybe you should stop
saying "sea bass"</font></b>

00:15:37.854 --> 00:15:38.901
<b><font color="#ffff00">and go after your friend.</font></b>

00:15:39.897 --> 00:15:41.023
<b><font color="#ffff00">This was so fun.</font></b>

00:15:42.024 --> 00:15:43.947
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'll just stay here
and say "sea bass" alone.</font></b>

00:15:51.826 --> 00:15:52.827
<b><font color="#ffff00">And I hate you.</font></b>

00:15:53.619 --> 00:15:55.587
<b><font color="#ffff00">What? I said he was cute.</font></b>

00:15:55.913 --> 00:15:57.711
<b><font color="#ffff00">Just shut up and drive.</font></b>

00:16:06.841 --> 00:16:08.521
<b><font color="#ffff00">You need to take the next left.</font></b>

00:16:09.302 --> 00:16:11.054
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Who's he?
- He's my intern.</font></b>

00:16:11.596 --> 00:16:13.394
<b><font color="#ffff00">- You have an intern?
- Oh, yeah.</font></b>

00:16:13.639 --> 00:16:15.516
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hello, Dr. Foster.</font></b>

00:16:15.641 --> 00:16:17.482
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's such a great honor
to be working with you.</font></b>

00:16:17.727 --> 00:16:19.855
<b><font color="#ffff00">Right. I have to call Erik.</font></b>

00:16:19.979 --> 00:16:21.322
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh, take a right.</font></b>

00:16:23.566 --> 00:16:24.658
<b><font color="#ffff00">And a left.</font></b>

00:16:26.736 --> 00:16:29.706
<b><font color="#ffff00">I have totally
mastered driving in London.</font></b>

00:16:29.822 --> 00:16:33.326
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hi, Erik. It's me again.
Where are you?</font></b>

00:16:33.451 --> 00:16:36.371
<b><font color="#ffff00">I came here because you said you were
onto something, and then you vanish.</font></b>

00:16:36.496 --> 00:16:37.918
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm here at Stonehenge</font></b>

00:16:38.080 --> 00:16:41.254
<b><font color="#ffff00">for what has been an interesting
unfolding of events today.</font></b>

00:16:41.584 --> 00:16:43.086
<b><font color="#ffff00">The police were called to the scene</font></b>

00:16:43.169 --> 00:16:44.671
<b><font color="#ffff00">shortly after 11 A.M.
this morning</font></b>

00:16:44.754 --> 00:16:48.179
<b><font color="#ffff00">after a seemingly harmless
rambler approached the area</font></b>

00:16:48.257 --> 00:16:51.056
<b><font color="#ffff00">then, decided to strip naked
and effectively</font></b>

00:16:51.177 --> 00:16:53.305
<b><font color="#ffff00">terrorize tourists there
with scientific equipment</font></b>

00:16:53.596 --> 00:16:56.315
<b><font color="#ffff00">whilst shouting that he
was trying to save them.</font></b>

00:16:56.849 --> 00:17:00.695
<b><font color="#ffff00">The man, later identified as noted
astrophysicist Dr. Erik Selvig</font></b>

00:17:00.770 --> 00:17:03.398
<b><font color="#ffff00">has been called in
for questioning by police.</font></b>

00:17:05.650 --> 00:17:07.448
<b><font color="#ffff00">Come on, this is exciting.</font></b>

00:17:08.110 --> 00:17:09.737
<b><font color="#ffff00">Look! The intern is excited.</font></b>

00:17:09.946 --> 00:17:11.072
<b><font color="#ffff00">"Ian."</font></b>

00:17:11.197 --> 00:17:12.665
<b><font color="#ffff00">Do you want the phase meter?</font></b>

00:17:12.740 --> 00:17:14.208
<b><font color="#ffff00">- No.
- Bring the phase meter.</font></b>

00:17:15.117 --> 00:17:16.164
<b><font color="#ffff00">The toaster-looking thing.</font></b>

00:17:16.327 --> 00:17:18.876
<b><font color="#ffff00">Yeah.
I know what the phase meter is.</font></b>

00:17:26.546 --> 00:17:28.924
<b><font color="#ffff00">How do I change the
ringtone on this thing?</font></b>

00:17:29.006 --> 00:17:30.974
<b><font color="#ffff00">An astrophysicist with three degrees</font></b>

00:17:31.050 --> 00:17:32.802
<b><font color="#ffff00">should be able to change
her own ringtone.</font></b>

00:17:32.927 --> 00:17:34.395
<b><font color="#ffff00">Why are you calling me?</font></b>

00:17:34.470 --> 00:17:36.723
<b><font color="#ffff00">I didn't want to shout.
Intern says it's this way.</font></b>

00:17:36.806 --> 00:17:38.854
<b><font color="#ffff00">- "Ian." My name is Ian.
- Shh.</font></b>

00:17:52.363 --> 00:17:56.038
<b><font color="#ffff00">I am not getting stabbed
in the name of science.</font></b>

00:17:56.158 --> 00:17:57.660
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's okay, we're Americans.</font></b>

00:17:57.743 --> 00:17:59.711
<b><font color="#ffff00">Is that supposed to
make them like us?</font></b>

00:17:59.787 --> 00:18:01.539
<b><font color="#ffff00">- They'll make it go away.
- Shh.</font></b>

00:18:03.874 --> 00:18:05.467
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh, they're kids.</font></b>

00:18:05.793 --> 00:18:06.919
<b><font color="#ffff00">Are you the police?</font></b>

00:18:07.545 --> 00:18:10.264
<b><font color="#ffff00">No, we're scientists.
Well, I am.</font></b>

00:18:10.548 --> 00:18:11.640
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thanks.</font></b>

00:18:11.757 --> 00:18:13.430
<b><font color="#ffff00">We just found it.</font></b>

00:18:15.636 --> 00:18:16.853
<b><font color="#ffff00">Can you show us?</font></b>

00:18:43.331 --> 00:18:45.834
<b><font color="#ffff00">That doesn't seem right.</font></b>

00:19:02.725 --> 00:19:03.897
<b><font color="#ffff00">Where'd it go?</font></b>

00:19:17.448 --> 00:19:18.449
<b><font color="#ffff00">That's...</font></b>

00:19:19.033 --> 00:19:20.125
<b><font color="#ffff00">That's incredible!</font></b>

00:19:33.839 --> 00:19:35.261
<b><font color="#ffff00">What happened?</font></b>

00:19:35.424 --> 00:19:36.801
<b><font color="#ffff00">Sometimes they come back.</font></b>

00:19:37.093 --> 00:19:38.515
<b><font color="#ffff00">Sometimes they don't.</font></b>

00:19:41.263 --> 00:19:42.685
<b><font color="#ffff00">I want to throw something!</font></b>

00:19:42.807 --> 00:19:43.933
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane, give me your shoe.</font></b>

00:19:46.435 --> 00:19:48.733
<b><font color="#ffff00">I haven't seen readings
like this since...</font></b>

00:19:49.355 --> 00:19:50.356
<b><font color="#ffff00">Since...</font></b>

00:19:50.481 --> 00:19:51.482
<b><font color="#ffff00">New Mexico?</font></b>

00:19:56.028 --> 00:19:57.951
<b><font color="#ffff00">Don't touch anything!</font></b>

00:20:00.700 --> 00:20:02.293
<b><font color="#ffff00">Give me your shoe.</font></b>

00:20:07.915 --> 00:20:09.132
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh.</font></b>

00:20:23.347 --> 00:20:25.816
<b><font color="#ffff00">Were those the car keys?</font></b>

00:20:54.170 --> 00:20:55.672
<b><font color="#ffff00">Whoa. Ah!</font></b>

00:20:57.673 --> 00:20:59.175
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh!</font></b>

00:21:03.512 --> 00:21:04.513
<b><font color="#ffff00">Darcy!</font></b>

00:21:51.727 --> 00:21:52.728
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh!</font></b>

00:23:05.551 --> 00:23:07.804
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Aether awakens us.</font></b>

00:23:07.970 --> 00:23:11.440
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Convergence returns.</font></b>

00:23:26.155 --> 00:23:27.828
<b><font color="#ffff00">You're late.</font></b>

00:23:28.908 --> 00:23:32.162
<b><font color="#ffff00">Merriment can sometimes be a
heavier burden than battle.</font></b>

00:23:32.328 --> 00:23:33.968
<b><font color="#ffff00">Then you're doing
one of them incorrectly.</font></b>

00:23:34.747 --> 00:23:36.670
<b><font color="#ffff00">Perhaps.</font></b>

00:23:36.832 --> 00:23:38.675
<b><font color="#ffff00">How fare the stars?</font></b>

00:23:38.834 --> 00:23:40.507
<b><font color="#ffff00">Still shining.</font></b>

00:23:40.669 --> 00:23:43.468
<b><font color="#ffff00">From here, I can see nine
realms and ten trillion souls.</font></b>

00:23:48.344 --> 00:23:51.097
<b><font color="#ffff00">Do you recall what I taught
you of the Convergence?</font></b>

00:23:51.263 --> 00:23:52.355
<b><font color="#ffff00">Yes.</font></b>

00:23:52.598 --> 00:23:54.851
<b><font color="#ffff00">The alignment of the worlds.</font></b>

00:23:55.017 --> 00:23:56.735
<b><font color="#ffff00">It approaches, doesn't it?</font></b>

00:23:56.977 --> 00:24:00.857
<b><font color="#ffff00">The universe hasn't seen this
marvel since before my watch began.</font></b>

00:24:01.899 --> 00:24:05.119
<b><font color="#ffff00">Few can sense it.
Even fewer can see it.</font></b>

00:24:06.528 --> 00:24:09.077
<b><font color="#ffff00">But while its effects
can be dangerous,</font></b>

00:24:09.907 --> 00:24:12.751
<b><font color="#ffff00">it is truly beautiful.</font></b>

00:24:14.036 --> 00:24:15.504
<b><font color="#ffff00">I see nothing.</font></b>

00:24:15.579 --> 00:24:19.209
<b><font color="#ffff00">Or, perhaps, that is not
the beauty you seek.</font></b>

00:24:25.047 --> 00:24:26.390
<b><font color="#ffff00">How is she?</font></b>

00:24:26.548 --> 00:24:28.471
<b><font color="#ffff00">She's quite clever,
your mortal.</font></b>

00:24:28.592 --> 00:24:29.844
<b><font color="#ffff00">She doesn't know it yet,</font></b>

00:24:29.927 --> 00:24:32.430
<b><font color="#ffff00">but she studies
the Convergence as well.</font></b>

00:24:32.596 --> 00:24:33.813
<b><font color="#ffff00">Even...</font></b>

00:24:35.557 --> 00:24:36.979
<b><font color="#ffff00">What?</font></b>

00:24:39.812 --> 00:24:41.234
<b><font color="#ffff00">I can't see her.</font></b>

00:25:20.644 --> 00:25:23.238
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane!</font></b>

00:25:23.814 --> 00:25:25.111
<b><font color="#ffff00">Where the hell were you?</font></b>

00:25:25.441 --> 00:25:26.863
<b><font color="#ffff00">Tell me you didn't call the police.</font></b>

00:25:26.942 --> 00:25:28.068
<b><font color="#ffff00">What was I supposed to do?</font></b>

00:25:28.193 --> 00:25:29.991
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Not call the police.
- I was freaking out.</font></b>

00:25:30.070 --> 00:25:31.287
<b><font color="#ffff00">You call the cops,
they call the Feds.</font></b>

00:25:31.363 --> 00:25:33.286
<b><font color="#ffff00">Next thing you know, we have
S.H.I.E.L.D. crawling all over</font></b>

00:25:33.490 --> 00:25:34.958
<b><font color="#ffff00">- "Area 51-ing" the place.
- Jane.</font></b>

00:25:35.034 --> 00:25:37.128
<b><font color="#ffff00">We had a stable gravitation anomaly.</font></b>

00:25:37.202 --> 00:25:38.499
<b><font color="#ffff00">We had unimpeded access.</font></b>

00:25:38.829 --> 00:25:41.127
<b><font color="#ffff00">Our only competition
was ten years old!</font></b>

00:25:41.290 --> 00:25:42.837
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane!
You were gone for five hours.</font></b>

00:25:43.375 --> 00:25:44.627
<b><font color="#ffff00">What?</font></b>

00:25:51.467 --> 00:25:53.140
<b><font color="#ffff00">That's weird.</font></b>

00:26:14.698 --> 00:26:16.120
<b><font color="#ffff00">Typical</font></b>

00:26:16.867 --> 00:26:17.914
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane.</font></b>

00:26:20.579 --> 00:26:23.332
<b><font color="#ffff00">Sorry. I just needed
to make sure you were real.</font></b>

00:26:23.499 --> 00:26:25.001
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's been a very strange day.</font></b>

00:26:25.167 --> 00:26:26.669
<b><font color="#ffff00">I am. Jane, what...</font></b>

00:26:27.086 --> 00:26:28.133
<b><font color="#ffff00">Where were you?</font></b>

00:26:28.337 --> 00:26:29.338
<b><font color="#ffff00">Where were you?</font></b>

00:26:30.255 --> 00:26:31.598
<b><font color="#ffff00">Heimdall cannot see you.</font></b>

00:26:31.757 --> 00:26:33.509
<b><font color="#ffff00">I was right here where you left me.</font></b>

00:26:33.759 --> 00:26:35.853
<b><font color="#ffff00">I was waiting,
and then I was crying</font></b>

00:26:35.969 --> 00:26:37.516
<b><font color="#ffff00">and then I went out
looking for you.</font></b>

00:26:37.679 --> 00:26:39.226
<b><font color="#ffff00">You said you were coming back.</font></b>

00:26:39.389 --> 00:26:41.733
<b><font color="#ffff00">I know. I know, but the
Bifrost was destroyed.</font></b>

00:26:41.892 --> 00:26:43.439
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Nine Realms erupted into chaos.</font></b>

00:26:43.560 --> 00:26:45.733
<b><font color="#ffff00">Wars were raging,
marauders were pillaging.</font></b>

00:26:46.271 --> 00:26:47.898
<b><font color="#ffff00">I had to put an
end to the slaughter.</font></b>

00:26:49.483 --> 00:26:53.238
<b><font color="#ffff00">As excuses go, it's not terrible.</font></b>

00:26:53.320 --> 00:26:56.164
<b><font color="#ffff00">But I saw you on TV.
You were in New York!</font></b>

00:26:57.074 --> 00:26:59.793
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane, I fought to protect you
from the dangers of my world</font></b>

00:26:59.868 --> 00:27:01.666
<b><font color="#ffff00">but I was wrong.</font></b>

00:27:01.829 --> 00:27:03.706
<b><font color="#ffff00">I was a fool.</font></b>

00:27:04.581 --> 00:27:08.051
<b><font color="#ffff00">But I believe that fate
brought us together.</font></b>

00:27:10.129 --> 00:27:13.178
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane, I don't know where you were,
or what happened, but I do know this...</font></b>

00:27:14.007 --> 00:27:15.008
<b><font color="#ffff00">What?</font></b>

00:27:16.260 --> 00:27:17.307
<b><font color="#ffff00">I know...</font></b>

00:27:18.512 --> 00:27:19.638
<b><font color="#ffff00">You do?</font></b>

00:27:21.140 --> 00:27:22.232
<b><font color="#ffff00">Do what?</font></b>

00:27:22.850 --> 00:27:23.976
<b><font color="#ffff00">What?</font></b>

00:27:24.560 --> 00:27:25.561
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hey!</font></b>

00:27:27.312 --> 00:27:28.780
<b><font color="#ffff00">Is this you?</font></b>

00:27:33.152 --> 00:27:34.574
<b><font color="#ffff00">Uh, we're kind of in the middle
of something here.</font></b>

00:27:34.987 --> 00:27:37.661
<b><font color="#ffff00">Um, I'm pretty sure
we are getting arrested.</font></b>

00:27:37.906 --> 00:27:38.907
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hold that thought.</font></b>

00:27:40.325 --> 00:27:43.920
<b><font color="#ffff00">Look at you, still all
muscly and everything.</font></b>

00:27:43.996 --> 00:27:45.669
<b><font color="#ffff00">How's space?</font></b>

00:27:45.747 --> 00:27:47.875
<b><font color="#ffff00">Space is fine.</font></b>

00:27:48.000 --> 00:27:49.252
<b><font color="#ffff00">Excuse me.</font></b>

00:27:49.418 --> 00:27:50.539
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Are you Jane Foster?
- Yes.</font></b>

00:27:50.586 --> 00:27:51.587
<b><font color="#ffff00">Do you know this man?</font></b>

00:27:53.130 --> 00:27:54.256
<b><font color="#ffff00">He's my intern.</font></b>

00:27:55.424 --> 00:27:56.596
<b><font color="#ffff00">My intern's intern.</font></b>

00:27:56.717 --> 00:27:58.719
<b><font color="#ffff00">This is private property and you're
trespassing, the lot of you.</font></b>

00:27:58.802 --> 00:28:00.099
<b><font color="#ffff00">You'll have to come with me.</font></b>

00:28:05.893 --> 00:28:06.894
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane.</font></b>

00:28:07.686 --> 00:28:09.654
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Jane.
- Thor?</font></b>

00:28:09.980 --> 00:28:10.981
<b><font color="#ffff00">Are you all right?</font></b>

00:28:11.190 --> 00:28:12.362
<b><font color="#ffff00">What just happened?</font></b>

00:28:12.941 --> 00:28:15.444
<b><font color="#ffff00">Place your hands
on your heads. Step back.</font></b>

00:28:15.527 --> 00:28:16.608
<b><font color="#ffff00">This woman is unwell.</font></b>

00:28:16.653 --> 00:28:17.654
<b><font color="#ffff00">She's dangerous.</font></b>

00:28:18.655 --> 00:28:19.998
<b><font color="#ffff00">So am I.</font></b>

00:28:20.991 --> 00:28:23.119
<b><font color="#ffff00">Requesting armed response
officers to scene.</font></b>

00:28:23.493 --> 00:28:25.120
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Hold on to me.
- What are you doing?</font></b>

00:28:33.462 --> 00:28:35.510
<b><font color="#ffff00">Holy shit.</font></b>

00:29:02.991 --> 00:29:05.039
<b><font color="#ffff00">We have to do that again.</font></b>

00:29:05.494 --> 00:29:06.495
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hi.</font></b>

00:29:09.331 --> 00:29:11.504
<b><font color="#ffff00">Welcome to Asgard.</font></b>

00:29:32.938 --> 00:29:35.532
<b><font color="#ffff00">Look upon my legacy, Algrim.</font></b>

00:29:37.359 --> 00:29:39.737
<b><font color="#ffff00">I can barely remember a time
before the light.</font></b>

00:29:40.487 --> 00:29:43.661
<b><font color="#ffff00">Our survival will be your legacy.</font></b>

00:29:45.617 --> 00:29:49.292
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Asgardians will suffer
as we have suffered.</font></b>

00:29:49.371 --> 00:29:50.623
<b><font color="#ffff00">I will reclaim the Aether.</font></b>

00:29:50.706 --> 00:29:51.958
<b><font color="#ffff00">I will restore our world.</font></b>

00:29:52.040 --> 00:29:54.759
<b><font color="#ffff00">And I will put an end
to this poisoned universe.</font></b>

00:30:03.051 --> 00:30:04.052
<b><font color="#ffff00">What's that?</font></b>

00:30:04.136 --> 00:30:05.183
<b><font color="#ffff00">Be still.</font></b>

00:30:12.728 --> 00:30:15.106
<b><font color="#ffff00">This is not of Earth.
What is it?</font></b>

00:30:15.897 --> 00:30:17.570
<b><font color="#ffff00">We do not know.</font></b>

00:30:18.275 --> 00:30:22.246
<b><font color="#ffff00">But she will not survive the amount
of energy surging within her.</font></b>

00:30:27.784 --> 00:30:29.464
<b><font color="#ffff00">That's a quantum field
generator, isn't it?</font></b>

00:30:30.078 --> 00:30:31.921
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's a soul forge.</font></b>

00:30:32.039 --> 00:30:35.259
<b><font color="#ffff00">Does a soul forge transfer molecular
energy from one place to another?</font></b>

00:30:38.128 --> 00:30:39.175
<b><font color="#ffff00">Yes.</font></b>

00:30:39.296 --> 00:30:41.048
<b><font color="#ffff00">Quantum field generator.</font></b>

00:30:42.174 --> 00:30:45.098
<b><font color="#ffff00">My words are mere noises to you
that you ignore them completely?</font></b>

00:30:45.260 --> 00:30:46.386
<b><font color="#ffff00">She is ill.</font></b>

00:30:46.511 --> 00:30:48.764
<b><font color="#ffff00">She is mortal.</font></b>

00:30:48.930 --> 00:30:50.477
<b><font color="#ffff00">Illness is their defining trait.</font></b>

00:30:50.599 --> 00:30:52.279
<b><font color="#ffff00">I brought her here
because we can help her.</font></b>

00:30:52.309 --> 00:30:54.232
<b><font color="#ffff00">She does not belong here in Asgard</font></b>

00:30:54.394 --> 00:30:57.773
<b><font color="#ffff00">any more than a goat
belongs at a banquet table.</font></b>

00:30:57.939 --> 00:30:59.532
<b><font color="#ffff00">Did he just...</font></b>

00:30:59.608 --> 00:31:01.201
<b><font color="#ffff00">Who do you think you are?</font></b>

00:31:01.276 --> 00:31:03.825
<b><font color="#ffff00">I am Odin, King of Asgard.</font></b>

00:31:03.987 --> 00:31:05.534
<b><font color="#ffff00">Protector of the Nine Realms.</font></b>

00:31:06.406 --> 00:31:08.283
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh. Well, I'm...</font></b>

00:31:08.450 --> 00:31:11.294
<b><font color="#ffff00">I know very well who you are,
Jane Foster.</font></b>

00:31:12.245 --> 00:31:13.622
<b><font color="#ffff00">You told your dad about me?</font></b>

00:31:14.498 --> 00:31:15.966
<b><font color="#ffff00">Something is within her, Father.</font></b>

00:31:16.083 --> 00:31:17.404
<b><font color="#ffff00">Something I have not seen before.</font></b>

00:31:17.417 --> 00:31:18.634
<b><font color="#ffff00">Her world has its healers.</font></b>

00:31:18.752 --> 00:31:20.672
<b><font color="#ffff00">They are called "doctors."
Let them deal with it.</font></b>

00:31:20.796 --> 00:31:22.594
<b><font color="#ffff00">Guards, take her back to Midgard.</font></b>

00:31:23.965 --> 00:31:25.467
<b><font color="#ffff00">No, I would not...</font></b>

00:31:27.302 --> 00:31:28.394
<b><font color="#ffff00">touch her.</font></b>

00:31:28.512 --> 00:31:29.809
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane, are you all right?</font></b>

00:31:30.347 --> 00:31:31.473
<b><font color="#ffff00">Yeah.</font></b>

00:31:35.185 --> 00:31:36.437
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's impossible.</font></b>

00:31:37.646 --> 00:31:40.399
<b><font color="#ffff00">The infection...
It's defending her.</font></b>

00:31:41.024 --> 00:31:42.321
<b><font color="#ffff00">No.</font></b>

00:31:42.818 --> 00:31:44.491
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's defending itself.</font></b>

00:31:45.529 --> 00:31:47.531
<b><font color="#ffff00">Come with me.</font></b>

00:31:47.656 --> 00:31:51.456
<b><font color="#ffff00">There are relics that
pre-date the universe itself.</font></b>

00:31:51.618 --> 00:31:55.498
<b><font color="#ffff00">What lies within her
appears to be one of them.</font></b>

00:31:56.498 --> 00:31:59.001
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Nine Realms are not eternal.</font></b>

00:31:59.167 --> 00:32:00.339
<b><font color="#ffff00">They had a dawn</font></b>

00:32:00.502 --> 00:32:01.674
<b><font color="#ffff00">as they will have a dusk.</font></b>

00:32:03.004 --> 00:32:04.005
<b><font color="#ffff00">But before that dawn</font></b>

00:32:04.172 --> 00:32:10.521
<b><font color="#ffff00">the dark forces, the Dark Elves,
reigned absolute and unchallenged.</font></b>

00:32:12.472 --> 00:32:13.769
<b><font color="#ffff00">"Born of eternal night</font></b>

00:32:13.890 --> 00:32:16.734
<b><font color="#ffff00">"the Dark Elves come
to steal away the light."</font></b>

00:32:17.185 --> 00:32:20.610
<b><font color="#ffff00">I know these stories.
Mother told them to us as children.</font></b>

00:32:20.689 --> 00:32:23.943
<b><font color="#ffff00">Their leader Malekith made a
weapon out of that darkness</font></b>

00:32:24.025 --> 00:32:25.618
<b><font color="#ffff00">and it was called the Aether.</font></b>

00:32:25.694 --> 00:32:28.743
<b><font color="#ffff00">While the other relics
often appear as stones</font></b>

00:32:28.822 --> 00:32:31.496
<b><font color="#ffff00">the Aether is fluid
and everchanging.</font></b>

00:32:31.658 --> 00:32:34.252
<b><font color="#ffff00">It changes matter into dark matter.</font></b>

00:32:34.369 --> 00:32:37.964
<b><font color="#ffff00">It seeks out host bodies, drawing
strength from their life-force.</font></b>

00:32:39.207 --> 00:32:42.177
<b><font color="#ffff00">Malekith sought to use
the Aether's power</font></b>

00:32:42.335 --> 00:32:46.090
<b><font color="#ffff00">to return the universe
to one of darkness.</font></b>

00:32:46.756 --> 00:32:49.384
<b><font color="#ffff00">But, after eternities of bloodshed</font></b>

00:32:49.468 --> 00:32:52.062
<b><font color="#ffff00">my father Bor finally triumphed</font></b>

00:32:52.220 --> 00:32:56.726
<b><font color="#ffff00">ushering in a peace
that lasted thousands of years.</font></b>

00:32:57.726 --> 00:32:58.898
<b><font color="#ffff00">What happened?</font></b>

00:33:00.187 --> 00:33:02.110
<b><font color="#ffff00">He killed them all.</font></b>

00:33:02.230 --> 00:33:04.403
<b><font color="#ffff00">Are you certain?</font></b>

00:33:04.483 --> 00:33:06.563
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Aether was said to have
been destroyed with them,</font></b>

00:33:06.568 --> 00:33:07.820
<b><font color="#ffff00">and yet here it is.</font></b>

00:33:09.237 --> 00:33:11.410
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Dark Elves are dead.</font></b>

00:33:12.073 --> 00:33:15.543
<b><font color="#ffff00">Does your book happen to mention
how to get it out of me?</font></b>

00:33:15.619 --> 00:33:16.620
<b><font color="#ffff00">No.</font></b>

00:33:17.621 --> 00:33:19.248
<b><font color="#ffff00">It does not.</font></b>

00:33:29.090 --> 00:33:31.969
<b><font color="#ffff00">The worlds are nearly aligned.</font></b>

00:33:37.390 --> 00:33:39.142
<b><font color="#ffff00">You will be the last of the Kursed.</font></b>

00:33:40.310 --> 00:33:41.937
<b><font color="#ffff00">Let my life be sacrificed.</font></b>

00:33:42.896 --> 00:33:45.615
<b><font color="#ffff00">It is no less than our people did,</font></b>

00:33:46.274 --> 00:33:47.446
<b><font color="#ffff00">or you have done.</font></b>

00:33:55.242 --> 00:33:57.210
<b><font color="#ffff00">You will become darkness.</font></b>

00:33:58.411 --> 00:34:02.132
<b><font color="#ffff00">Cursed to this existence
until it consumes you.</font></b>

00:34:07.379 --> 00:34:11.259
<b><font color="#ffff00">Until then, no power our enemies
possess can stop you.</font></b>

00:34:14.344 --> 00:34:21.148
<b><font color="#ffff00">I will tear down their defenses and
ensure your return to a universe reborn.</font></b>

00:34:43.373 --> 00:34:46.377
<b><font color="#ffff00">Acting as caretakers to these
scoundrels is beneath us.</font></b>

00:34:46.543 --> 00:34:48.637
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh, please!
If they were beneath you,</font></b>

00:34:48.712 --> 00:34:50.840
<b><font color="#ffff00">my rotund friend,
they'd all be dead.</font></b>

00:35:05.520 --> 00:35:07.522
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Keep in line!
- Move it!</font></b>

00:35:09.024 --> 00:35:12.699
<b><font color="#ffff00">Odin continues to
bring me new friends.</font></b>

00:35:13.069 --> 00:35:14.821
<b><font color="#ffff00">How thoughtful.</font></b>

00:35:15.071 --> 00:35:18.541
<b><font color="#ffff00">The books I sent,
do they not interest you?</font></b>

00:35:19.034 --> 00:35:22.334
<b><font color="#ffff00">Is that how I am to while
away eternity? Reading?</font></b>

00:35:22.412 --> 00:35:25.541
<b><font color="#ffff00">I've done everything in my power
to make you comfortable, Loki.</font></b>

00:35:25.624 --> 00:35:26.671
<b><font color="#ffff00">Have you?</font></b>

00:35:27.709 --> 00:35:29.552
<b><font color="#ffff00">Does Odin share your concern?</font></b>

00:35:31.004 --> 00:35:32.551
<b><font color="#ffff00">Does Thor?</font></b>

00:35:32.714 --> 00:35:36.344
<b><font color="#ffff00">It must be so inconvenient, them
asking after me day and night.</font></b>

00:35:36.426 --> 00:35:39.555
<b><font color="#ffff00">You know full well it was your
actions that brought you here.</font></b>

00:35:40.096 --> 00:35:41.439
<b><font color="#ffff00">My actions?</font></b>

00:35:41.598 --> 00:35:44.852
<b><font color="#ffff00">I was merely giving truth to the lie
that I had been fed my entire life...</font></b>

00:35:44.934 --> 00:35:46.607
<b><font color="#ffff00">That I was born to be a king.</font></b>

00:35:46.686 --> 00:35:48.654
<b><font color="#ffff00">A king?</font></b>

00:35:48.730 --> 00:35:50.732
<b><font color="#ffff00">A true king admits his faults.</font></b>

00:35:50.857 --> 00:35:52.297
<b><font color="#ffff00">What of the lives you took on Earth?</font></b>

00:35:52.442 --> 00:35:54.035
<b><font color="#ffff00">A mere handful
compared to the number</font></b>

00:35:54.110 --> 00:35:55.908
<b><font color="#ffff00">that Odin has taken himself.</font></b>

00:35:56.071 --> 00:35:58.745
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Your father...
- He's not my father!</font></b>

00:36:01.618 --> 00:36:03.837
<b><font color="#ffff00">Then am I not your mother?</font></b>

00:36:09.042 --> 00:36:11.010
<b><font color="#ffff00">You're not.</font></b>

00:36:14.798 --> 00:36:19.770
<b><font color="#ffff00">You're always so perceptive
about everyone but yourself.</font></b>

00:36:34.943 --> 00:36:38.117
<b><font color="#ffff00">When you came for me,
you knew I was in trouble.</font></b>

00:36:38.238 --> 00:36:39.490
<b><font color="#ffff00">Heimdall had lost sight of you.</font></b>

00:36:39.614 --> 00:36:41.287
<b><font color="#ffff00">You were no longer on Earth.</font></b>

00:36:41.449 --> 00:36:42.746
<b><font color="#ffff00">How is that possible?</font></b>

00:36:42.951 --> 00:36:44.919
<b><font color="#ffff00">I believe you were
and you weren't.</font></b>

00:36:44.994 --> 00:36:47.873
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Nine Realms
travel within Yggdrasil</font></b>

00:36:48.164 --> 00:36:51.418
<b><font color="#ffff00">orbiting Midgard much the way
your planets orbit the sun.</font></b>

00:36:51.584 --> 00:36:55.714
<b><font color="#ffff00">And every 5,000 years,
the worlds align perfectly</font></b>

00:36:55.797 --> 00:36:58.016
<b><font color="#ffff00">and we call this the Convergence.</font></b>

00:37:00.135 --> 00:37:03.810
<b><font color="#ffff00">During this time, the borders
between worlds become blurred.</font></b>

00:37:04.472 --> 00:37:07.271
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's possible you found
one of these points.</font></b>

00:37:09.310 --> 00:37:11.529
<b><font color="#ffff00">We are lucky that it remained open.</font></b>

00:37:11.688 --> 00:37:15.943
<b><font color="#ffff00">Once the worlds pass
out of alignment</font></b>

00:37:17.360 --> 00:37:19.408
<b><font color="#ffff00">then the connection is lost.</font></b>

00:37:32.167 --> 00:37:34.545
<b><font color="#ffff00">I like the way you explain things.</font></b>

00:37:36.838 --> 00:37:38.215
<b><font color="#ffff00">What's going to happen to me?</font></b>

00:37:38.381 --> 00:37:39.974
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'll find a way to save you, Jane.</font></b>

00:37:40.133 --> 00:37:43.307
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Your father said there was...
- My father doesn't know everything.</font></b>

00:37:43.511 --> 00:37:45.184
<b><font color="#ffff00">Don't let him hear you say that.</font></b>

00:37:46.556 --> 00:37:47.853
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane Foster...</font></b>

00:37:47.932 --> 00:37:49.275
<b><font color="#ffff00">Please meet Frigga,</font></b>

00:37:49.350 --> 00:37:51.273
<b><font color="#ffff00">Queen of Asgard, and my mother.</font></b>

00:37:54.022 --> 00:37:55.490
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hi.</font></b>

00:38:44.614 --> 00:38:46.036
<b><font color="#ffff00">Move!</font></b>

00:39:32.620 --> 00:39:33.872
<b><font color="#ffff00">To the dungeons!</font></b>

00:39:34.247 --> 00:39:35.248
<b><font color="#ffff00">Come on!</font></b>

00:39:59.063 --> 00:40:01.486
<b><font color="#ffff00">You might want to take
the stairs to the left.</font></b>

00:40:12.535 --> 00:40:13.878
<b><font color="#ffff00">The prisons.</font></b>

00:40:14.037 --> 00:40:15.835
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Loki...
- Go.</font></b>

00:40:15.997 --> 00:40:17.840
<b><font color="#ffff00">I will look after her.</font></b>

00:40:29.260 --> 00:40:30.821
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's as if they resent
being imprisoned!</font></b>

00:40:34.849 --> 00:40:37.693
<b><font color="#ffff00">There's no pleasing some creatures.</font></b>

00:40:45.693 --> 00:40:47.854
<b><font color="#ffff00">Return to your cells, no
further harm will come to you.</font></b>

00:40:48.029 --> 00:40:49.201
<b><font color="#ffff00">You have my word.</font></b>

00:40:51.032 --> 00:40:53.376
<b><font color="#ffff00">Very well, you do
not have my word.</font></b>

00:41:03.252 --> 00:41:05.254
<b><font color="#ffff00">Send a squadron
to the weapons vault.</font></b>

00:41:05.380 --> 00:41:07.929
<b><font color="#ffff00">Defend it at all costs.
Secure the dungeon.</font></b>

00:41:08.091 --> 00:41:09.684
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Odin.
- Frigga.</font></b>

00:41:10.551 --> 00:41:11.552
<b><font color="#ffff00">Go!</font></b>

00:41:12.345 --> 00:41:13.597
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's a skirmish.</font></b>

00:41:13.721 --> 00:41:14.893
<b><font color="#ffff00">Nothing to fear.</font></b>

00:41:14.973 --> 00:41:16.475
<b><font color="#ffff00">You've never been a very good liar.</font></b>

00:41:17.433 --> 00:41:18.480
<b><font color="#ffff00">Take her to your chambers.</font></b>

00:41:18.559 --> 00:41:20.436
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'll come for you when it's safe.</font></b>

00:41:20.561 --> 00:41:22.063
<b><font color="#ffff00">You take care.</font></b>

00:41:22.146 --> 00:41:23.267
<b><font color="#ffff00">Despite all I have survived,</font></b>

00:41:24.065 --> 00:41:26.784
<b><font color="#ffff00">my queen still worries over me.</font></b>

00:41:26.985 --> 00:41:28.111
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's only because
I worry over you</font></b>

00:41:28.236 --> 00:41:30.079
<b><font color="#ffff00">that you have survived.</font></b>

00:41:32.573 --> 00:41:33.790
<b><font color="#ffff00">Listen to me now.</font></b>

00:41:33.950 --> 00:41:36.920
<b><font color="#ffff00">I need you to do everything
I ask, no questions.</font></b>

00:41:37.036 --> 00:41:38.208
<b><font color="#ffff00">Yes, ma'am.</font></b>

00:42:19.245 --> 00:42:20.417
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh!</font></b>

00:45:50.790 --> 00:45:52.167
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Ow!
- Ah!</font></b>

00:46:47.763 --> 00:46:50.892
<b><font color="#ffff00">The throne of Asgard
is destroyed! To the king!</font></b>

00:47:06.699 --> 00:47:07.700
<b><font color="#ffff00">Frigga.</font></b>

00:47:16.500 --> 00:47:18.923
<b><font color="#ffff00">Stand down, creature,</font></b>

00:47:19.086 --> 00:47:20.713
<b><font color="#ffff00">and you may still survive this.</font></b>

00:47:20.796 --> 00:47:22.890
<b><font color="#ffff00">I have survived worse, woman.</font></b>

00:47:24.342 --> 00:47:25.719
<b><font color="#ffff00">Who are you?</font></b>

00:47:26.260 --> 00:47:28.308
<b><font color="#ffff00">I am Malekith.</font></b>

00:47:28.471 --> 00:47:31.099
<b><font color="#ffff00">And I would have what is mine.</font></b>

00:47:43.361 --> 00:47:44.362
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ah!</font></b>

00:48:01.754 --> 00:48:03.927
<b><font color="#ffff00">You have taken something, child.</font></b>

00:48:04.965 --> 00:48:06.012
<b><font color="#ffff00">Give it back.</font></b>

00:48:20.398 --> 00:48:21.490
<b><font color="#ffff00">Witch!</font></b>

00:48:25.194 --> 00:48:26.696
<b><font color="#ffff00">Where is the Aether?</font></b>

00:48:26.821 --> 00:48:29.119
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'll never tell you.</font></b>

00:48:30.116 --> 00:48:31.333
<b><font color="#ffff00">I believe you.</font></b>

00:48:33.828 --> 00:48:36.001
<b><font color="#ffff00">No!</font></b>

00:52:02.745 --> 00:52:04.918
<b><font color="#ffff00">The universe rotates
on a 5,000-year cycle</font></b>

00:52:05.789 --> 00:52:08.167
<b><font color="#ffff00">and once a cycle,
all the worlds align.</font></b>

00:52:08.834 --> 00:52:11.758
<b><font color="#ffff00">Imagine... Imagine that
this is our world.</font></b>

00:52:12.504 --> 00:52:14.552
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh, thank you.
And this is another world.</font></b>

00:52:14.715 --> 00:52:16.683
<b><font color="#ffff00">Normally, they're separate.</font></b>

00:52:16.842 --> 00:52:18.560
<b><font color="#ffff00">But during the Alignment,</font></b>

00:52:18.636 --> 00:52:22.186
<b><font color="#ffff00">everything is connected,
all nine realms.</font></b>

00:52:22.348 --> 00:52:24.521
<b><font color="#ffff00">All nine realms are passing
through each other</font></b>

00:52:24.600 --> 00:52:26.944
<b><font color="#ffff00">and gravity, light,
and even matter,</font></b>

00:52:27.227 --> 00:52:29.650
<b><font color="#ffff00">is crashing from one
world to the other.</font></b>

00:52:31.982 --> 00:52:35.907
<b><font color="#ffff00">But if this happens to us now,
the result will be cataclysmic.</font></b>

00:52:35.986 --> 00:52:40.492
<b><font color="#ffff00">My gravimetric spikes can stabilize
the focal point of the Convergence.</font></b>

00:52:41.200 --> 00:52:43.498
<b><font color="#ffff00">This time, the Alignment</font></b>

00:52:43.577 --> 00:52:46.581
<b><font color="#ffff00">and all the other worlds
would just pass us by.</font></b>

00:52:46.747 --> 00:52:48.249
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's beautiful.</font></b>

00:52:49.750 --> 00:52:51.923
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's simple. Any questions?</font></b>

00:52:55.047 --> 00:52:56.094
<b><font color="#ffff00">Yeah.</font></b>

00:52:56.548 --> 00:52:59.267
<b><font color="#ffff00">Can I have my shoe back?</font></b>

00:53:07.017 --> 00:53:11.022
<b><font color="#ffff00">Heal. You will need your
strength to reclaim the Aether.</font></b>

00:53:11.522 --> 00:53:15.117
<b><font color="#ffff00">And when you wake,
we will kill them all.</font></b>

00:53:50.686 --> 00:53:51.983
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane Foster?</font></b>

00:53:53.647 --> 00:53:55.820
<b><font color="#ffff00">You need to come with us.</font></b>

00:53:57.067 --> 00:54:00.162
<b><font color="#ffff00">We are still unable to
restore the palace shields.</font></b>

00:54:00.279 --> 00:54:01.701
<b><font color="#ffff00">Our artillery cannot detect them.</font></b>

00:54:01.822 --> 00:54:03.620
<b><font color="#ffff00">Even Heimdall cannot see them.</font></b>

00:54:06.994 --> 00:54:10.919
<b><font color="#ffff00">My king, we are all but defenseless.</font></b>

00:54:13.500 --> 00:54:14.968
<b><font color="#ffff00">She's your prisoner now?</font></b>

00:54:17.337 --> 00:54:18.680
<b><font color="#ffff00">Leave us.</font></b>

00:54:27.681 --> 00:54:29.854
<b><font color="#ffff00">I do not wish to fight with you.</font></b>

00:54:30.350 --> 00:54:32.102
<b><font color="#ffff00">Nor I with you.</font></b>

00:54:32.186 --> 00:54:34.029
<b><font color="#ffff00">But I intend to pursue Malekith.</font></b>

00:54:34.188 --> 00:54:35.485
<b><font color="#ffff00">We possess the Aether.</font></b>

00:54:36.148 --> 00:54:37.365
<b><font color="#ffff00">Malekith will come to us.</font></b>

00:54:37.524 --> 00:54:39.526
<b><font color="#ffff00">Yes, and he will destroy us.</font></b>

00:54:39.610 --> 00:54:41.738
<b><font color="#ffff00">You overestimate the
power of these creatures.</font></b>

00:54:41.862 --> 00:54:44.206
<b><font color="#ffff00">No, I value our people's lives.</font></b>

00:54:44.364 --> 00:54:47.664
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'll take Jane to the Dark World, and
draw the enemy away from Asgard.</font></b>

00:54:48.410 --> 00:54:50.629
<b><font color="#ffff00">When Malekith pulls
the Aether from Jane,</font></b>

00:54:50.704 --> 00:54:52.706
<b><font color="#ffff00">it will be exposed and vulnerable.</font></b>

00:54:52.873 --> 00:54:54.671
<b><font color="#ffff00">And I will destroy it and him.</font></b>

00:54:56.710 --> 00:54:59.463
<b><font color="#ffff00">If you fail, you risk this weapon</font></b>

00:54:59.546 --> 00:55:01.389
<b><font color="#ffff00">falling into the hands
of our enemies.</font></b>

00:55:01.507 --> 00:55:03.885
<b><font color="#ffff00">The risk is far greater
if we do nothing.</font></b>

00:55:04.009 --> 00:55:05.977
<b><font color="#ffff00">His ship could be over
our heads right now,</font></b>

00:55:06.178 --> 00:55:07.395
<b><font color="#ffff00">we would never even know it.</font></b>

00:55:07.554 --> 00:55:08.726
<b><font color="#ffff00">If and when he comes</font></b>

00:55:08.806 --> 00:55:12.982
<b><font color="#ffff00">his men will fall on
10,000 Asgardian blades.</font></b>

00:55:13.060 --> 00:55:14.482
<b><font color="#ffff00">And how many of our men
shall fall on theirs?</font></b>

00:55:14.603 --> 00:55:16.571
<b><font color="#ffff00">As many as are needed!</font></b>

00:55:19.650 --> 00:55:20.742
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ah!</font></b>

00:55:25.531 --> 00:55:27.078
<b><font color="#ffff00">We will fight!</font></b>

00:55:29.576 --> 00:55:32.125
<b><font color="#ffff00">Till the last Asgardian breath.</font></b>

00:55:32.913 --> 00:55:35.962
<b><font color="#ffff00">Till the last drop
of Asgardian blood.</font></b>

00:55:38.085 --> 00:55:41.214
<b><font color="#ffff00">Then how are you
different from Malekith?</font></b>

00:55:44.424 --> 00:55:47.018
<b><font color="#ffff00">The difference, my son,
is that I will win.</font></b>

00:56:01.316 --> 00:56:04.115
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane isn't calling me back,
Erik isn't calling me back,</font></b>

00:56:04.236 --> 00:56:06.159
<b><font color="#ffff00">stupid S.H.I.E.L.D.
isn't calling me back.</font></b>

00:56:06.280 --> 00:56:08.123
<b><font color="#ffff00">- What's S.H.I.E.L.D?
- It's a secret.</font></b>

00:56:08.198 --> 00:56:10.121
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hey, Erik, it's Darcy again.</font></b>

00:56:10.242 --> 00:56:13.041
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thor came back,
he took Jane to Asgard,</font></b>

00:56:13.287 --> 00:56:16.757
<b><font color="#ffff00">and I'm not sure
what I'm supposed to do.</font></b>

00:56:16.832 --> 00:56:18.755
<b><font color="#ffff00">Something else
went missing this week</font></b>

00:56:18.834 --> 00:56:21.963
<b><font color="#ffff00">when astrophysicist Dr. Erik Selvig</font></b>

00:56:22.087 --> 00:56:25.637
<b><font color="#ffff00">notable for his involvement in
the alien invasion of New York</font></b>

00:56:25.799 --> 00:56:27.096
<b><font color="#ffff00">streaked nude across...</font></b>

00:56:27.259 --> 00:56:29.808
<b><font color="#ffff00">Darcy, you really
need to look at this.</font></b>

00:56:29.970 --> 00:56:31.142
<b><font color="#ffff00">Your friend, Erik...</font></b>

00:56:31.221 --> 00:56:32.973
<b><font color="#ffff00">What was his last name again?</font></b>

00:56:33.932 --> 00:56:37.311
<b><font color="#ffff00">And began shouting at visitors
to the historic site.</font></b>

00:56:37.477 --> 00:56:39.525
<b><font color="#ffff00">He was later taken
into police custody</font></b>

00:56:40.147 --> 00:56:42.445
<b><font color="#ffff00">for psychiatric evaluation.</font></b>

00:56:42.608 --> 00:56:44.656
<b><font color="#ffff00">Police are still
refusing to confirm...</font></b>

00:56:55.162 --> 00:56:57.210
<b><font color="#ffff00">You were not at Odin's war council.</font></b>

00:56:57.331 --> 00:56:59.675
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Bifrost is closed
by your father's orders.</font></b>

00:56:59.875 --> 00:57:01.172
<b><font color="#ffff00">No one is to come</font></b>

00:57:01.251 --> 00:57:02.548
<b><font color="#ffff00">or to go.</font></b>

00:57:04.630 --> 00:57:07.349
<b><font color="#ffff00">We face an enemy
that is invisible even to me.</font></b>

00:57:07.507 --> 00:57:11.228
<b><font color="#ffff00">What use is a guardian such as that?</font></b>

00:57:12.679 --> 00:57:15.432
<b><font color="#ffff00">Malekith will return,
you know this.</font></b>

00:57:17.976 --> 00:57:19.023
<b><font color="#ffff00">I need your help.</font></b>

00:57:19.645 --> 00:57:23.240
<b><font color="#ffff00">I cannot overrule my king's wishes.
Not even for you.</font></b>

00:57:23.357 --> 00:57:24.984
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm not asking you to.</font></b>

00:57:25.192 --> 00:57:27.536
<b><font color="#ffff00">The realms need their Allfather
strong and unchallenged</font></b>

00:57:27.694 --> 00:57:30.243
<b><font color="#ffff00">whether he is or not.</font></b>

00:57:30.405 --> 00:57:32.123
<b><font color="#ffff00">But he is blinded, Heimdall</font></b>

00:57:32.199 --> 00:57:33.951
<b><font color="#ffff00">by hatred and by grief.</font></b>

00:57:34.034 --> 00:57:35.707
<b><font color="#ffff00">As are we all.</font></b>

00:57:35.786 --> 00:57:37.003
<b><font color="#ffff00">I see clearly enough.</font></b>

00:57:37.079 --> 00:57:38.706
<b><font color="#ffff00">The risks are too great.</font></b>

00:57:38.997 --> 00:57:41.716
<b><font color="#ffff00">Everything we do from
here on is a risk.</font></b>

00:57:41.875 --> 00:57:43.593
<b><font color="#ffff00">There is no other way.</font></b>

00:57:47.547 --> 00:57:49.766
<b><font color="#ffff00">What do you require of me?</font></b>

00:57:49.883 --> 00:57:53.433
<b><font color="#ffff00">What I'm about to ask of you
is treason of the highest order.</font></b>

00:57:53.720 --> 00:57:57.770
<b><font color="#ffff00">Success will bring us exile and
failure shall mean our death.</font></b>

00:58:00.644 --> 00:58:04.740
<b><font color="#ffff00">Malekith knew the Aether was here.
He can sense its power.</font></b>

00:58:05.273 --> 00:58:07.446
<b><font color="#ffff00">If we do nothing,
he will come for it again</font></b>

00:58:07.609 --> 00:58:11.739
<b><font color="#ffff00">but this time, lay waste
to all of Asgard.</font></b>

00:58:12.739 --> 00:58:14.741
<b><font color="#ffff00">We must move
Jane off-world.</font></b>

00:58:14.908 --> 00:58:16.581
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Bifrost has been shut down</font></b>

00:58:16.702 --> 00:58:18.420
<b><font color="#ffff00">and the Tesseract
locked away in the vault.</font></b>

00:58:18.578 --> 00:58:22.708
<b><font color="#ffff00">There are other paths off Asgard.
Ways known only to a few.</font></b>

00:58:22.791 --> 00:58:24.714
<b><font color="#ffff00">One, actually.</font></b>

00:58:26.795 --> 00:58:28.547
<b><font color="#ffff00">No.</font></b>

00:58:32.926 --> 00:58:36.180
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thor. After all this time</font></b>

00:58:36.263 --> 00:58:38.937
<b><font color="#ffff00">and now you come to visit me.</font></b>

00:58:40.142 --> 00:58:41.439
<b><font color="#ffff00">Why?</font></b>

00:58:42.769 --> 00:58:45.818
<b><font color="#ffff00">Have you come to gloat?
To mock?</font></b>

00:58:45.939 --> 00:58:47.566
<b><font color="#ffff00">Loki, enough.</font></b>

00:58:47.983 --> 00:58:49.826
<b><font color="#ffff00">No more illusions.</font></b>

00:58:56.992 --> 00:58:59.086
<b><font color="#ffff00">Now you see me, brother.</font></b>

00:59:07.794 --> 00:59:09.512
<b><font color="#ffff00">Did she suffer?</font></b>

00:59:09.629 --> 00:59:11.973
<b><font color="#ffff00">I did not come here
to share our grief.</font></b>

00:59:12.090 --> 00:59:15.185
<b><font color="#ffff00">Instead I offer you the chance
of a far richer sacrament.</font></b>

00:59:16.595 --> 00:59:17.812
<b><font color="#ffff00">Go on.</font></b>

00:59:17.971 --> 00:59:20.645
<b><font color="#ffff00">I know you seek vengeance
as much as I do.</font></b>

00:59:20.724 --> 00:59:23.694
<b><font color="#ffff00">You help me escape Asgard
and I will grant it to you.</font></b>

00:59:23.977 --> 00:59:25.354
<b><font color="#ffff00">Vengeance</font></b>

00:59:25.520 --> 00:59:27.943
<b><font color="#ffff00">and afterward, this cell.</font></b>

00:59:34.696 --> 00:59:39.497
<b><font color="#ffff00">You must be truly desperate
to come to me for help.</font></b>

00:59:41.161 --> 00:59:42.754
<b><font color="#ffff00">What makes you think
you can trust me?</font></b>

00:59:42.829 --> 00:59:44.251
<b><font color="#ffff00">I don't.</font></b>

00:59:45.957 --> 00:59:47.049
<b><font color="#ffff00">Mother did.</font></b>

00:59:48.335 --> 00:59:50.838
<b><font color="#ffff00">But you should know that when
we fought each other in the past,</font></b>

00:59:51.671 --> 00:59:53.139
<b><font color="#ffff00">I did so with a glimmer of hope</font></b>

00:59:53.215 --> 00:59:55.092
<b><font color="#ffff00">that my brother
was still in there somewhere.</font></b>

00:59:56.718 --> 00:59:59.187
<b><font color="#ffff00">That hope no longer exists
to protect you.</font></b>

01:00:00.013 --> 01:00:03.392
<b><font color="#ffff00">You betray me, and I will kill you.</font></b>

01:00:06.061 --> 01:00:07.404
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hmm.</font></b>

01:00:08.897 --> 01:00:10.615
<b><font color="#ffff00">When do we start?</font></b>

01:00:10.690 --> 01:00:12.033
<b><font color="#ffff00">He will betray you.</font></b>

01:00:12.109 --> 01:00:13.736
<b><font color="#ffff00">He will try.</font></b>

01:00:18.323 --> 01:00:20.701
<b><font color="#ffff00">This is so unlike you, brother.</font></b>

01:00:20.867 --> 01:00:22.869
<b><font color="#ffff00">So clandestine.</font></b>

01:00:22.994 --> 01:00:25.235
<b><font color="#ffff00">Are you sure you wouldn't
rather just punch your way out?</font></b>

01:00:25.997 --> 01:00:27.874
<b><font color="#ffff00">If you keep speaking,
I just might.</font></b>

01:00:27.999 --> 01:00:29.842
<b><font color="#ffff00">Fine. As you wish.</font></b>

01:00:30.210 --> 01:00:31.382
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm not even here.</font></b>

01:00:32.712 --> 01:00:34.214
<b><font color="#ffff00">Is this better?</font></b>

01:00:34.381 --> 01:00:36.884
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's better company at least.</font></b>

01:00:37.008 --> 01:00:40.933
<b><font color="#ffff00">Still, we could be
less conspicuous.</font></b>

01:00:42.514 --> 01:00:44.858
<b><font color="#ffff00">Mmm, brother, you look ravishing.</font></b>

01:00:46.852 --> 01:00:49.401
<b><font color="#ffff00">It will hurt no less
when I kill you in this form.</font></b>

01:00:49.563 --> 01:00:52.737
<b><font color="#ffff00">Very well. Perhaps you
prefer one of your new companions</font></b>

01:00:52.899 --> 01:00:54.947
<b><font color="#ffff00">given that you seem
to like them so much.</font></b>

01:00:55.527 --> 01:00:57.529
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh, this is much better.</font></b>

01:00:57.612 --> 01:00:58.613
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ooh.</font></b>

01:00:58.947 --> 01:01:01.575
<b><font color="#ffff00">The costume is a bit much.
So tight.</font></b>

01:01:01.741 --> 01:01:03.038
<b><font color="#ffff00">But the confidence...</font></b>

01:01:03.201 --> 01:01:05.624
<b><font color="#ffff00">I can feel the
righteousness surging.</font></b>

01:01:05.787 --> 01:01:08.256
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hey, do you want to have a
rousing discussion about truth?</font></b>

01:01:08.707 --> 01:01:09.924
<b><font color="#ffff00">Honor? Patriotism?</font></b>

01:01:10.000 --> 01:01:11.001
<b><font color="#ffff00">God bless Amer...</font></b>

01:01:13.712 --> 01:01:15.055
<b><font color="#ffff00">What?</font></b>

01:01:19.551 --> 01:01:21.929
<b><font color="#ffff00">You could at least furnish
me with a weapon.</font></b>

01:01:22.095 --> 01:01:23.972
<b><font color="#ffff00">My dagger, something.</font></b>

01:01:29.477 --> 01:01:30.729
<b><font color="#ffff00">At last.</font></b>

01:01:30.812 --> 01:01:32.530
<b><font color="#ffff00">A little common sense.</font></b>

01:01:38.653 --> 01:01:41.202
<b><font color="#ffff00">And I thought you liked tricks.</font></b>

01:01:41.281 --> 01:01:45.832
<b><font color="#ffff00">Well, what then? Your lovely mortal is
being guarded by a legion of Einherjar</font></b>

01:01:45.994 --> 01:01:47.746
<b><font color="#ffff00">who will see you coming
from miles away.</font></b>

01:01:47.829 --> 01:01:49.547
<b><font color="#ffff00">I won't be the one
who comes for her.</font></b>

01:01:57.339 --> 01:01:58.340
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm not hungry.</font></b>

01:01:59.132 --> 01:02:00.884
<b><font color="#ffff00">What the...</font></b>

01:02:00.967 --> 01:02:03.220
<b><font color="#ffff00">Good. Let's go.</font></b>

01:02:08.600 --> 01:02:09.647
<b><font color="#ffff00">You're...</font></b>

01:02:09.809 --> 01:02:11.777
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm Loki,
you may have heard of me.</font></b>

01:02:11.853 --> 01:02:14.402
<b><font color="#ffff00">That was for New York.</font></b>

01:02:14.481 --> 01:02:15.858
<b><font color="#ffff00">I like her.</font></b>

01:02:15.982 --> 01:02:17.655
<b><font color="#ffff00">And what of the Allfather?</font></b>

01:02:18.318 --> 01:02:22.039
<b><font color="#ffff00">It is my sworn duty to notify him
of crimes against the throne.</font></b>

01:02:22.155 --> 01:02:25.785
<b><font color="#ffff00">You called me here
on an urgent matter.</font></b>

01:02:26.826 --> 01:02:27.827
<b><font color="#ffff00">What is it?</font></b>

01:02:28.286 --> 01:02:29.583
<b><font color="#ffff00">Treason, my lord.</font></b>

01:02:29.663 --> 01:02:31.006
<b><font color="#ffff00">Whose?</font></b>

01:02:31.706 --> 01:02:32.753
<b><font color="#ffff00">Mine.</font></b>

01:02:33.500 --> 01:02:35.002
<b><font color="#ffff00">My king!</font></b>

01:02:35.085 --> 01:02:37.087
<b><font color="#ffff00">The mortal has been taken.</font></b>

01:02:40.966 --> 01:02:41.967
<b><font color="#ffff00">Stop Thor.</font></b>

01:02:42.050 --> 01:02:44.178
<b><font color="#ffff00">By any means necessary.</font></b>

01:02:46.888 --> 01:02:49.391
<b><font color="#ffff00">There they are! Take them.</font></b>

01:02:49.516 --> 01:02:50.483
<b><font color="#ffff00">On my command.</font></b>

01:02:50.558 --> 01:02:52.777
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'll hold them off.
Take her.</font></b>

01:02:53.395 --> 01:02:54.817
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font></b>

01:02:57.524 --> 01:02:59.777
<b><font color="#ffff00">Betray him, and I'll kill you.</font></b>

01:03:02.028 --> 01:03:04.622
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's good to see you, too, Sif.</font></b>

01:03:10.203 --> 01:03:14.549
<b><font color="#ffff00">Assuming you can get Loki's help
and you can free this mortal</font></b>

01:03:14.666 --> 01:03:16.168
<b><font color="#ffff00">what good would it do?</font></b>

01:03:16.251 --> 01:03:19.130
<b><font color="#ffff00">We'd all be dead the minute we
step one foot outside the palace.</font></b>

01:03:19.212 --> 01:03:22.432
<b><font color="#ffff00">That, my friend, is why we
won't be leaving by foot.</font></b>

01:03:26.553 --> 01:03:28.305
<b><font color="#ffff00">I will give you as
much time as I can.</font></b>

01:03:28.388 --> 01:03:30.231
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thank you, my friend.</font></b>

01:03:34.394 --> 01:03:37.568
<b><font color="#ffff00">If you even think
about betraying him...</font></b>

01:03:37.689 --> 01:03:39.316
<b><font color="#ffff00">You'll kill me?</font></b>

01:03:39.399 --> 01:03:41.401
<b><font color="#ffff00">Evidently, there will be a line.</font></b>

01:03:56.708 --> 01:03:58.802
<b><font color="#ffff00">I thought you said you knew
how to fly this thing.</font></b>

01:03:58.960 --> 01:04:00.758
<b><font color="#ffff00">I said, "How hard could it be?"</font></b>

01:04:04.132 --> 01:04:05.133
<b><font color="#ffff00">They're on the ship!</font></b>

01:04:05.967 --> 01:04:07.264
<b><font color="#ffff00">Get to the ship!</font></b>

01:04:10.972 --> 01:04:13.566
<b><font color="#ffff00">Well, whatever you're doing, brother,
I suggest you do it faster.</font></b>

01:04:13.641 --> 01:04:16.019
<b><font color="#ffff00">Shut up, Loki.</font></b>

01:04:17.187 --> 01:04:18.387
<b><font color="#ffff00">You must have missed something.</font></b>

01:04:18.396 --> 01:04:21.115
<b><font color="#ffff00">No, I didn't. I'm pressing
every button on this thing.</font></b>

01:04:21.191 --> 01:04:22.784
<b><font color="#ffff00">No, don't hit it.
Just press it gently.</font></b>

01:04:22.901 --> 01:04:24.744
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm pressing it gently,
it's not working!</font></b>

01:04:27.864 --> 01:04:28.865
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ha, ha!</font></b>

01:04:32.494 --> 01:04:34.087
<b><font color="#ffff00">Get him! Get him!</font></b>

01:05:02.649 --> 01:05:05.152
<b><font color="#ffff00">- I think you missed a column.
- Shut up!</font></b>

01:05:12.409 --> 01:05:13.661
<b><font color="#ffff00">Look, why don't
you let me take over?</font></b>

01:05:13.743 --> 01:05:14.995
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm clearly the better pilot.</font></b>

01:05:15.286 --> 01:05:17.209
<b><font color="#ffff00">Is that right?
Well, out of the two of us,</font></b>

01:05:17.330 --> 01:05:18.832
<b><font color="#ffff00">which one can actually fly?</font></b>

01:05:29.342 --> 01:05:30.935
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh, dear. Is she dead?</font></b>

01:05:31.010 --> 01:05:32.011
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane.</font></b>

01:05:32.804 --> 01:05:33.805
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm okay.</font></b>

01:05:35.765 --> 01:05:36.937
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ah!</font></b>

01:05:40.937 --> 01:05:42.280
<b><font color="#ffff00">Not a word.</font></b>

01:05:44.399 --> 01:05:45.776
<b><font color="#ffff00">Now they're following us.</font></b>

01:05:51.156 --> 01:05:52.282
<b><font color="#ffff00">Now they're firing at us.</font></b>

01:05:52.449 --> 01:05:53.792
<b><font color="#ffff00">Yeah, thank you
for the commentary, Loki,</font></b>

01:05:53.867 --> 01:05:55.210
<b><font color="#ffff00">it's not at all distracting!</font></b>

01:05:59.747 --> 01:06:02.375
<b><font color="#ffff00">Well done. You just
decapitated your grandfather.</font></b>

01:06:13.803 --> 01:06:15.146
<b><font color="#ffff00">You know, this is wonderful.</font></b>

01:06:15.263 --> 01:06:17.561
<b><font color="#ffff00">This is a tremendous idea.</font></b>

01:06:17.724 --> 01:06:20.819
<b><font color="#ffff00">Let's steal the biggest,
most obvious ship in the universe</font></b>

01:06:20.977 --> 01:06:22.229
<b><font color="#ffff00">and escape in that.</font></b>

01:06:22.312 --> 01:06:23.484
<b><font color="#ffff00">Flying around the city,</font></b>

01:06:23.563 --> 01:06:25.941
<b><font color="#ffff00">smashing into everything in
sight so everyone can see us.</font></b>

01:06:26.065 --> 01:06:27.783
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's brilliant, Thor!
It's truly brilliant!</font></b>

01:06:42.373 --> 01:06:43.920
<b><font color="#ffff00">I see your time in the dungeons</font></b>

01:06:44.000 --> 01:06:46.594
<b><font color="#ffff00">has made you no less graceful, Loki.</font></b>

01:06:50.798 --> 01:06:52.766
<b><font color="#ffff00">You lied to me.</font></b>

01:06:54.010 --> 01:06:55.387
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm impressed.</font></b>

01:06:55.470 --> 01:06:56.938
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm glad you're pleased.</font></b>

01:06:57.013 --> 01:06:58.014
<b><font color="#ffff00">Now, do as you promised.</font></b>

01:06:58.097 --> 01:06:59.940
<b><font color="#ffff00">And take us to your secret pathway.</font></b>

01:07:23.164 --> 01:07:24.711
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Fandral.
- Right.</font></b>

01:07:28.419 --> 01:07:29.420
<b><font color="#ffff00">For Asgard.</font></b>

01:07:35.051 --> 01:07:36.143
<b><font color="#ffff00">Nothing personal, boys.</font></b>

01:07:51.442 --> 01:07:52.819
<b><font color="#ffff00">Loki...</font></b>

01:07:52.902 --> 01:07:56.247
<b><font color="#ffff00">if it were easy,
everyone would do it.</font></b>

01:07:56.322 --> 01:07:58.324
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Are you mad?
- Possibly.</font></b>

01:08:13.923 --> 01:08:15.516
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ta-da!</font></b>

01:08:21.055 --> 01:08:24.400
<b><font color="#ffff00">We must strike now.</font></b>

01:08:25.435 --> 01:08:26.436
<b><font color="#ffff00">No.</font></b>

01:08:28.062 --> 01:08:33.694
<b><font color="#ffff00">Asgard is meaningless.</font></b>

01:08:37.905 --> 01:08:39.828
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Aether has found its way home.</font></b>

01:08:55.590 --> 01:08:59.094
<b><font color="#ffff00">What I could do with the power
that flows through those veins.</font></b>

01:08:59.177 --> 01:09:01.851
<b><font color="#ffff00">It would consume you.</font></b>

01:09:02.805 --> 01:09:04.398
<b><font color="#ffff00">She's holding up all right.</font></b>

01:09:05.224 --> 01:09:06.350
<b><font color="#ffff00">For now.</font></b>

01:09:06.893 --> 01:09:09.442
<b><font color="#ffff00">She's strong in ways
you'd never even know.</font></b>

01:09:09.562 --> 01:09:10.905
<b><font color="#ffff00">Say goodbye.</font></b>

01:09:10.980 --> 01:09:12.778
<b><font color="#ffff00">Not this day.</font></b>

01:09:12.899 --> 01:09:15.698
<b><font color="#ffff00">This day, the next,
a hundred years, it's nothing.</font></b>

01:09:16.944 --> 01:09:18.491
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's a heartbeat.</font></b>

01:09:18.905 --> 01:09:20.907
<b><font color="#ffff00">You'll never be ready.</font></b>

01:09:21.324 --> 01:09:22.844
<b><font color="#ffff00">The only woman
whose love you've prized</font></b>

01:09:22.909 --> 01:09:24.707
<b><font color="#ffff00">will be snatched from you.</font></b>

01:09:24.786 --> 01:09:26.083
<b><font color="#ffff00">And will that satisfy you?</font></b>

01:09:26.204 --> 01:09:27.751
<b><font color="#ffff00">Satisfaction is not
in my nature.</font></b>

01:09:27.830 --> 01:09:30.049
<b><font color="#ffff00">Surrender is not in mine.</font></b>

01:09:30.833 --> 01:09:32.335
<b><font color="#ffff00">- The son of Odin...
- No.</font></b>

01:09:32.418 --> 01:09:34.466
<b><font color="#ffff00">Not just of Odin.</font></b>

01:09:34.587 --> 01:09:36.931
<b><font color="#ffff00">You think you alone
were loved of Mother?</font></b>

01:09:37.090 --> 01:09:39.092
<b><font color="#ffff00">You had her tricks,
but I had her trust.</font></b>

01:09:39.217 --> 01:09:40.514
<b><font color="#ffff00">Trust?</font></b>

01:09:41.427 --> 01:09:42.929
<b><font color="#ffff00">Was that her last expression?</font></b>

01:09:43.554 --> 01:09:45.773
<b><font color="#ffff00">Trust?
When you let her die?</font></b>

01:09:45.890 --> 01:09:48.609
<b><font color="#ffff00">- What help were you in your cell?
- Who put me there?</font></b>

01:09:48.685 --> 01:09:50.107
<b><font color="#ffff00">Who put me there?</font></b>

01:09:50.228 --> 01:09:51.229
<b><font color="#ffff00">You know damn well!</font></b>

01:09:51.938 --> 01:09:53.690
<b><font color="#ffff00">You know damn well who!</font></b>

01:09:59.946 --> 01:10:02.620
<b><font color="#ffff00">She wouldn't want us to fight.</font></b>

01:10:03.741 --> 01:10:06.290
<b><font color="#ffff00">Well, she wouldn't
exactly be shocked.</font></b>

01:10:10.998 --> 01:10:13.501
<b><font color="#ffff00">I wish I could trust you.</font></b>

01:10:28.015 --> 01:10:29.983
<b><font color="#ffff00">Trust my rage.</font></b>

01:10:36.649 --> 01:10:39.528
<b><font color="#ffff00">You'll have to sign for your
father's belongings, Mr. Selvig.</font></b>

01:10:40.194 --> 01:10:41.366
<b><font color="#ffff00">What?</font></b>

01:10:41.487 --> 01:10:42.830
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh, yeah.</font></b>

01:10:42.905 --> 01:10:45.909
<b><font color="#ffff00">My father, Dr. Erik Selvig.</font></b>

01:10:47.618 --> 01:10:49.996
<b><font color="#ffff00">One man's leather wallet, brown.</font></b>

01:10:50.079 --> 01:10:52.548
<b><font color="#ffff00">One key ring, three keys.</font></b>

01:10:52.665 --> 01:10:54.588
<b><font color="#ffff00">Prescription medicine...</font></b>

01:10:55.334 --> 01:10:56.586
<b><font color="#ffff00">Various.</font></b>

01:10:59.255 --> 01:11:01.007
<b><font color="#ffff00">- And...
- Erik.</font></b>

01:11:02.592 --> 01:11:04.014
<b><font color="#ffff00">- These.
- Yeah.</font></b>

01:11:04.093 --> 01:11:05.310
<b><font color="#ffff00">Those.</font></b>

01:11:05.803 --> 01:11:07.100
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thank goodness.</font></b>

01:11:08.765 --> 01:11:09.982
<b><font color="#ffff00">Erik.</font></b>

01:11:11.768 --> 01:11:12.894
<b><font color="#ffff00">Yes?</font></b>

01:11:13.019 --> 01:11:14.692
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's, uh, Darcy.</font></b>

01:11:14.812 --> 01:11:15.904
<b><font color="#ffff00">Darcy.</font></b>

01:11:18.107 --> 01:11:19.905
<b><font color="#ffff00">So good to see you.</font></b>

01:11:20.026 --> 01:11:21.073
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh, I missed you, too.</font></b>

01:11:21.194 --> 01:11:22.616
<b><font color="#ffff00">How did you find me?</font></b>

01:11:22.695 --> 01:11:23.947
<b><font color="#ffff00">You were naked on TV.</font></b>

01:11:25.323 --> 01:11:27.451
<b><font color="#ffff00">Okay, time to go, lots to do.</font></b>

01:11:29.535 --> 01:11:31.537
<b><font color="#ffff00">Getting weird now.</font></b>

01:11:32.955 --> 01:11:35.083
<b><font color="#ffff00">I should not be left in
charge of stuff like this.</font></b>

01:11:35.208 --> 01:11:39.054
<b><font color="#ffff00">I don't get paid enough.
I don't get paid, period.</font></b>

01:11:39.128 --> 01:11:42.132
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm Ian by the way,
uh, Darcy's intern.</font></b>

01:11:42.298 --> 01:11:44.471
<b><font color="#ffff00">Yeah, I don't get paid either.</font></b>

01:11:45.343 --> 01:11:46.811
<b><font color="#ffff00">Are you all right?</font></b>

01:11:46.969 --> 01:11:48.812
<b><font color="#ffff00">I've had a god in my brain.</font></b>

01:11:50.139 --> 01:11:51.607
<b><font color="#ffff00">I don't recommend it.</font></b>

01:11:53.226 --> 01:11:55.524
<b><font color="#ffff00">Dr. Selvig, sir,
your gear is beeping at me.</font></b>

01:11:55.603 --> 01:11:57.981
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's happening.
It's sooner than I calculated.</font></b>

01:11:58.147 --> 01:11:59.774
<b><font color="#ffff00">Wait. What's happening?</font></b>

01:12:03.069 --> 01:12:04.742
<b><font color="#ffff00">Birds?</font></b>

01:12:04.862 --> 01:12:06.239
<b><font color="#ffff00">Birds are happening?</font></b>

01:12:06.322 --> 01:12:08.575
<b><font color="#ffff00">They're starlings.
It's called a murmuration.</font></b>

01:12:08.741 --> 01:12:10.914
<b><font color="#ffff00">My dad, he used to take me
bird watching as a kid.</font></b>

01:12:11.077 --> 01:12:12.579
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Nerd.
- Look!</font></b>

01:12:17.166 --> 01:12:19.339
<b><font color="#ffff00">Where did they go?</font></b>

01:12:32.139 --> 01:12:34.437
<b><font color="#ffff00">What the hell was that?</font></b>

01:12:34.934 --> 01:12:36.607
<b><font color="#ffff00">Why are you smiling?</font></b>

01:12:36.769 --> 01:12:38.009
<b><font color="#ffff00">There's nothing more reassuring</font></b>

01:12:38.062 --> 01:12:41.783
<b><font color="#ffff00">than realizing that the world
is crazier than you are.</font></b>

01:12:41.858 --> 01:12:44.737
<b><font color="#ffff00">Take me to Jane's lab.</font></b>

01:12:57.206 --> 01:12:58.674
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane.</font></b>

01:13:05.298 --> 01:13:06.641
<b><font color="#ffff00">Malekith.</font></b>

01:13:28.905 --> 01:13:30.828
<b><font color="#ffff00">All right. Are you ready?</font></b>

01:13:30.990 --> 01:13:32.242
<b><font color="#ffff00">I am.</font></b>

01:13:45.880 --> 01:13:47.882
<b><font color="#ffff00">You know, this plan of yours
is going to get us killed.</font></b>

01:13:48.007 --> 01:13:49.884
<b><font color="#ffff00">Yes, possibly.</font></b>

01:13:53.512 --> 01:13:54.873
<b><font color="#ffff00">You still don't trust me, brother?</font></b>

01:13:56.349 --> 01:13:57.646
<b><font color="#ffff00">Would you?</font></b>

01:14:06.567 --> 01:14:07.784
<b><font color="#ffff00">No, I wouldn't.</font></b>

01:14:12.573 --> 01:14:14.041
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thor!</font></b>

01:14:14.867 --> 01:14:16.460
<b><font color="#ffff00">No!</font></b>

01:14:25.753 --> 01:14:28.222
<b><font color="#ffff00">You really think I
cared about Frigga?</font></b>

01:14:28.297 --> 01:14:30.015
<b><font color="#ffff00">About any of you?</font></b>

01:14:33.010 --> 01:14:34.011
<b><font color="#ffff00">All I ever wanted</font></b>

01:14:35.513 --> 01:14:36.560
<b><font color="#ffff00">was you and Odin</font></b>

01:14:36.681 --> 01:14:37.773
<b><font color="#ffff00">dead at my feet!</font></b>

01:14:50.403 --> 01:14:51.404
<b><font color="#ffff00">Malekith!</font></b>

01:14:53.489 --> 01:14:55.491
<b><font color="#ffff00">I am Loki of Jotunheim,</font></b>

01:14:55.658 --> 01:14:57.581
<b><font color="#ffff00">and I bring you a gift.</font></b>

01:14:59.537 --> 01:15:01.380
<b><font color="#ffff00">I ask only one thing in return...</font></b>

01:15:01.455 --> 01:15:03.253
<b><font color="#ffff00">A good seat from which</font></b>

01:15:03.332 --> 01:15:05.332
<b><font color="#ffff00">to watch Asgard burn.</font></b>

01:15:05.501 --> 01:15:07.754
<b><font color="#ffff00">He is an enemy of Asgard.</font></b>

01:15:07.837 --> 01:15:10.590
<b><font color="#ffff00">He was a prisoner in their dungeons.</font></b>

01:15:24.812 --> 01:15:25.938
<b><font color="#ffff00">Look at me.</font></b>

01:16:23.954 --> 01:16:25.456
<b><font color="#ffff00">Loki! Now!</font></b>

01:17:45.870 --> 01:17:47.087
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ah!</font></b>

01:18:41.300 --> 01:18:42.301
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ah!</font></b>

01:19:39.692 --> 01:19:41.911
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Ah!
- No!</font></b>

01:19:51.161 --> 01:19:53.289
<b><font color="#ffff00">See you in hell, monster.</font></b>

01:20:12.141 --> 01:20:13.609
<b><font color="#ffff00">No. No, no, no.</font></b>

01:20:15.936 --> 01:20:18.189
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh, you fool, you didn't listen.</font></b>

01:20:18.272 --> 01:20:19.273
<b><font color="#ffff00">I know...</font></b>

01:20:20.316 --> 01:20:22.489
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm a fool, I'm a fool.</font></b>

01:20:22.568 --> 01:20:23.740
<b><font color="#ffff00">Stay with me, okay?</font></b>

01:20:23.819 --> 01:20:24.991
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm sorry.</font></b>

01:20:27.031 --> 01:20:29.250
<b><font color="#ffff00">- I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
- Shh...</font></b>

01:20:29.366 --> 01:20:30.663
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's okay.</font></b>

01:20:34.288 --> 01:20:35.790
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's all right.</font></b>

01:20:35.914 --> 01:20:39.418
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'll tell Father what
you did here today.</font></b>

01:20:42.504 --> 01:20:45.428
<b><font color="#ffff00">I didn't do it for him.</font></b>

01:20:53.974 --> 01:20:56.352
<b><font color="#ffff00">No!</font></b>

01:21:50.155 --> 01:21:52.203
<b><font color="#ffff00">He's going to unleash it.</font></b>

01:21:52.324 --> 01:21:57.501
<b><font color="#ffff00">Not just on Asgard, or on a star.
Malekith is going to destroy everything.</font></b>

01:21:57.621 --> 01:21:58.747
<b><font color="#ffff00">How?</font></b>

01:21:59.832 --> 01:22:01.004
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane, how?</font></b>

01:22:01.125 --> 01:22:04.345
<b><font color="#ffff00">I saw him on Earth.
Why would he go to Earth?</font></b>

01:22:04.920 --> 01:22:06.297
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Convergence.</font></b>

01:22:06.463 --> 01:22:07.635
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh, God.</font></b>

01:22:07.714 --> 01:22:10.154
<b><font color="#ffff00">None of this would have happened
if I hadn't found the Aether.</font></b>

01:22:10.926 --> 01:22:12.678
<b><font color="#ffff00">Then Malekith would've
only possessed it</font></b>

01:22:12.803 --> 01:22:14.476
<b><font color="#ffff00">that much sooner.</font></b>

01:22:14.555 --> 01:22:17.024
<b><font color="#ffff00">I only found it because
I was looking for you.</font></b>

01:22:17.641 --> 01:22:18.893
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane...</font></b>

01:22:20.519 --> 01:22:22.237
<b><font color="#ffff00">Now we're trapped here.</font></b>

01:22:28.777 --> 01:22:29.994
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's not me.</font></b>

01:22:31.280 --> 01:22:32.497
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hello?</font></b>

01:22:32.614 --> 01:22:33.831
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hi, Jane, it's Richard.</font></b>

01:22:33.991 --> 01:22:35.743
<b><font color="#ffff00">Richard? Where are you?</font></b>

01:22:35.868 --> 01:22:37.085
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm still at the office.</font></b>

01:22:37.202 --> 01:22:39.170
<b><font color="#ffff00">It's been a crazy day here today.</font></b>

01:22:39.246 --> 01:22:41.169
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Oh, my God, this is amazing.
- Is it?</font></b>

01:22:41.290 --> 01:22:42.507
<b><font color="#ffff00">I quite enjoyed our lunch</font></b>

01:22:42.583 --> 01:22:44.677
<b><font color="#ffff00">despite never actually
ordering anything.</font></b>

01:22:44.751 --> 01:22:46.173
<b><font color="#ffff00">How am I getting service here?</font></b>

01:22:46.253 --> 01:22:48.381
<b><font color="#ffff00">Is this a bad time?
Do you want me to try you later?</font></b>

01:22:48.505 --> 01:22:51.679
<b><font color="#ffff00">No, no, no. Please, whatever
you do, do not hang up the phone.</font></b>

01:22:52.551 --> 01:22:53.677
<b><font color="#ffff00">Okay, then.</font></b>

01:22:53.760 --> 01:22:56.138
<b><font color="#ffff00">I was just wondering
if you want to try again.</font></b>

01:22:56.221 --> 01:22:57.689
<b><font color="#ffff00">Uh, maybe dinner next time.</font></b>

01:22:57.764 --> 01:22:59.391
<b><font color="#ffff00">Uh, yeah, yeah, yeah.</font></b>

01:22:59.516 --> 01:23:01.769
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Just stay on the phone, okay?
- Yeah, I will.</font></b>

01:23:01.894 --> 01:23:03.862
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh, my God.</font></b>

01:23:07.733 --> 01:23:08.854
<b><font color="#ffff00">Am I interrupting something?</font></b>

01:23:08.901 --> 01:23:10.619
<b><font color="#ffff00">No, no, no. Nothing at all.</font></b>

01:23:10.777 --> 01:23:11.778
<b><font color="#ffff00">Come on.</font></b>

01:23:11.862 --> 01:23:12.954
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'm losing you there.
Are you in a tunnel?</font></b>

01:23:13.113 --> 01:23:14.535
<b><font color="#ffff00">Where are we going?</font></b>

01:23:14.615 --> 01:23:15.616
<b><font color="#ffff00">Hello?</font></b>

01:23:15.741 --> 01:23:17.584
<b><font color="#ffff00">Why are there so
many shoes in here?</font></b>

01:23:19.161 --> 01:23:21.004
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'll just text her.</font></b>

01:23:33.300 --> 01:23:34.472
<b><font color="#ffff00">So, who's Richard?</font></b>

01:23:34.635 --> 01:23:36.103
<b><font color="#ffff00">Really?</font></b>

01:23:44.436 --> 01:23:45.904
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Jane!
- Hey.</font></b>

01:23:45.979 --> 01:23:47.731
<b><font color="#ffff00">You can't just leave like that.</font></b>

01:23:47.814 --> 01:23:49.111
<b><font color="#ffff00">The whole world is going crazy.</font></b>

01:23:49.274 --> 01:23:51.117
<b><font color="#ffff00">All the stuff we saw is spreading.</font></b>

01:23:52.611 --> 01:23:54.454
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Did you go to a party?
- Erik?</font></b>

01:23:54.571 --> 01:23:58.246
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane! How wonderful.</font></b>

01:23:59.117 --> 01:24:00.164
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh!</font></b>

01:24:00.452 --> 01:24:02.332
<b><font color="#ffff00">- You've been to Asgard.
- Where are your pants?</font></b>

01:24:02.412 --> 01:24:04.164
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh, he, uh...
He says it helps him think.</font></b>

01:24:04.289 --> 01:24:05.882
<b><font color="#ffff00">Okay, well, I'm going to need
everything you got on this.</font></b>

01:24:05.958 --> 01:24:08.677
<b><font color="#ffff00">All the work you've been doing on
gravimetric anomalies, everything.</font></b>

01:24:08.794 --> 01:24:09.966
<b><font color="#ffff00">Okay.</font></b>

01:24:10.045 --> 01:24:12.139
<b><font color="#ffff00">Are you well, Erik?</font></b>

01:24:12.589 --> 01:24:14.091
<b><font color="#ffff00">Your brother's not coming, is he?</font></b>

01:24:15.092 --> 01:24:16.435
<b><font color="#ffff00">Loki is dead.</font></b>

01:24:16.510 --> 01:24:17.602
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh, thank God!</font></b>

01:24:18.762 --> 01:24:20.981
<b><font color="#ffff00">I... I meant, I'm so sorry.</font></b>

01:24:21.098 --> 01:24:22.645
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font></b>

01:24:46.248 --> 01:24:48.125
<b><font color="#ffff00">Forgive me, my liege.</font></b>

01:24:48.959 --> 01:24:51.462
<b><font color="#ffff00">I've returned from
the Dark World with news.</font></b>

01:24:53.922 --> 01:24:55.014
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thor?</font></b>

01:24:55.674 --> 01:25:00.100
<b><font color="#ffff00">There was no sign of Thor,
or the weapon, but...</font></b>

01:25:01.930 --> 01:25:03.147
<b><font color="#ffff00">What?</font></b>

01:25:06.101 --> 01:25:07.728
<b><font color="#ffff00">We found a body.</font></b>

01:25:12.441 --> 01:25:13.567
<b><font color="#ffff00">Loki.</font></b>

01:25:17.654 --> 01:25:19.497
<b><font color="#ffff00">Malekith is going to
fire the Aether at a spot</font></b>

01:25:19.656 --> 01:25:21.579
<b><font color="#ffff00">where all the nine worlds
are connecting.</font></b>

01:25:21.700 --> 01:25:24.169
<b><font color="#ffff00">Amplifying the weapon's impact.</font></b>

01:25:24.244 --> 01:25:25.666
<b><font color="#ffff00">For each additional world,</font></b>

01:25:25.787 --> 01:25:27.881
<b><font color="#ffff00">the power will increase
exponentially.</font></b>

01:25:28.165 --> 01:25:31.044
<b><font color="#ffff00">The effect would be universal.</font></b>

01:25:31.168 --> 01:25:32.795
<b><font color="#ffff00">But the Alignment is only temporary.</font></b>

01:25:32.878 --> 01:25:35.927
<b><font color="#ffff00">He must be in exactly the right
place at the right time.</font></b>

01:25:36.048 --> 01:25:37.721
<b><font color="#ffff00">Well, how do we know where that is?</font></b>

01:25:38.925 --> 01:25:41.348
<b><font color="#ffff00">We follow the directions.</font></b>

01:25:41.511 --> 01:25:42.763
<b><font color="#ffff00">This has happened before</font></b>

01:25:42.888 --> 01:25:46.233
<b><font color="#ffff00">thousands of years ago, and the
Ancients were there to see it.</font></b>

01:25:46.892 --> 01:25:48.269
<b><font color="#ffff00">All the great constructions,</font></b>

01:25:49.102 --> 01:25:51.821
<b><font color="#ffff00">the Mayans, the Chinese,
the Egyptians.</font></b>

01:25:51.897 --> 01:25:55.322
<b><font color="#ffff00">They made use of the gravitational
effects of the Convergence.</font></b>

01:25:55.400 --> 01:25:57.494
<b><font color="#ffff00">And they left us a map.</font></b>

01:25:57.569 --> 01:25:58.991
<b><font color="#ffff00">Stonehenge,</font></b>

01:26:00.447 --> 01:26:01.494
<b><font color="#ffff00">Snowdon,</font></b>

01:26:01.573 --> 01:26:02.745
<b><font color="#ffff00">the Great Orme.</font></b>

01:26:02.824 --> 01:26:04.701
<b><font color="#ffff00">These are all coordinates
taking us...</font></b>

01:26:06.078 --> 01:26:07.079
<b><font color="#ffff00">Here.</font></b>

01:26:09.581 --> 01:26:11.049
<b><font color="#ffff00">Greenwich?</font></b>

01:26:11.124 --> 01:26:13.752
<b><font color="#ffff00">The walls between worlds
will be almost non-existent.</font></b>

01:26:13.919 --> 01:26:15.240
<b><font color="#ffff00">Physics is going to go ballistic.</font></b>

01:26:15.295 --> 01:26:17.138
<b><font color="#ffff00">Increases and decreases in gravity,</font></b>

01:26:17.255 --> 01:26:18.723
<b><font color="#ffff00">spatial extrusions.</font></b>

01:26:18.799 --> 01:26:21.427
<b><font color="#ffff00">The very fabric of reality
is going to be torn apart.</font></b>

01:26:24.680 --> 01:26:26.933
<b><font color="#ffff00">I better get my pants.</font></b>

01:26:28.517 --> 01:26:29.860
<b><font color="#ffff00">Focus!
This is important.</font></b>

01:26:30.018 --> 01:26:31.486
<b><font color="#ffff00">We have to hammer them in
all around the site</font></b>

01:26:31.603 --> 01:26:33.901
<b><font color="#ffff00">and then Jane and Erik will
activate them from the tower.</font></b>

01:26:34.231 --> 01:26:35.699
<b><font color="#ffff00">They're taped together.</font></b>

01:26:35.899 --> 01:26:38.197
<b><font color="#ffff00">Do you even know
what these things do?</font></b>

01:26:38.568 --> 01:26:40.195
<b><font color="#ffff00">Uh... No.</font></b>

01:26:40.529 --> 01:26:41.530
<b><font color="#ffff00">Neither do I.</font></b>

01:26:46.535 --> 01:26:47.627
<b><font color="#ffff00">Shh!</font></b>

01:26:50.330 --> 01:26:52.332
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Come on, come on, come on!
- Right.</font></b>

01:27:05.137 --> 01:27:06.138
<b><font color="#ffff00">Holy...</font></b>

01:27:06.263 --> 01:27:07.264
<b><font color="#ffff00">Shit.</font></b>

01:27:19.776 --> 01:27:20.777
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ah!</font></b>

01:28:25.801 --> 01:28:28.099
<b><font color="#ffff00">You needn't have come
so far, Asgardian.</font></b>

01:28:28.220 --> 01:28:30.439
<b><font color="#ffff00">Death would've come to you
soon enough.</font></b>

01:28:30.555 --> 01:28:32.057
<b><font color="#ffff00">Not by your hand.</font></b>

01:28:32.140 --> 01:28:34.893
<b><font color="#ffff00">Your universe was never meant to be.</font></b>

01:28:34.976 --> 01:28:38.071
<b><font color="#ffff00">Your world and your family</font></b>

01:28:38.146 --> 01:28:40.274
<b><font color="#ffff00">will be extinguished!</font></b>

01:28:42.484 --> 01:28:43.906
<b><font color="#ffff00">We're running out of time.</font></b>

01:28:44.027 --> 01:28:46.371
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Almost there.
- Are you sure this is going to work?</font></b>

01:28:46.446 --> 01:28:49.040
<b><font color="#ffff00">These devices were made to detect
anomalies, not cause them.</font></b>

01:28:50.075 --> 01:28:51.167
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh, come on.</font></b>

01:28:56.414 --> 01:28:58.542
<b><font color="#ffff00">Come on, Darcy.</font></b>

01:29:08.969 --> 01:29:10.937
<b><font color="#ffff00">You know, with all that power,</font></b>

01:29:11.054 --> 01:29:12.556
<b><font color="#ffff00">I thought you'd hit harder.</font></b>

01:29:37.956 --> 01:29:39.048
<b><font color="#ffff00">Done.</font></b>

01:29:45.964 --> 01:29:48.683
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Convergence will be in
full effect in seven minutes.</font></b>

01:29:48.800 --> 01:29:51.001
<b><font color="#ffff00">That just means we have to
keep Malekith busy for eight.</font></b>

01:29:57.475 --> 01:29:59.352
<b><font color="#ffff00">Okay, you might want to
hold on to something.</font></b>

01:30:05.025 --> 01:30:06.402
<b><font color="#ffff00">That is awesome!</font></b>

01:30:06.484 --> 01:30:07.986
<b><font color="#ffff00">How did you do that?</font></b>

01:30:08.069 --> 01:30:09.366
<b><font color="#ffff00">Well, the gravitational fields</font></b>

01:30:09.446 --> 01:30:11.744
<b><font color="#ffff00">interact with the weak spots
between worlds, creating...</font></b>

01:30:11.823 --> 01:30:13.245
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ooh, get the guy with the sword!</font></b>

01:30:16.661 --> 01:30:18.538
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Oops.
- Let's go.</font></b>

01:30:18.663 --> 01:30:20.085
<b><font color="#ffff00">Um...</font></b>

01:30:20.498 --> 01:30:22.171
<b><font color="#ffff00">What the hell just happened?</font></b>

01:30:22.334 --> 01:30:23.961
<b><font color="#ffff00">Move!</font></b>

01:30:41.770 --> 01:30:43.067
<b><font color="#ffff00">What are you all doing?</font></b>

01:30:43.188 --> 01:30:44.861
<b><font color="#ffff00">You need to get out of here, now!</font></b>

01:30:44.981 --> 01:30:46.528
<b><font color="#ffff00">You're joking, right?</font></b>

01:30:46.650 --> 01:30:47.617
<b><font color="#ffff00">That's Thor out there.</font></b>

01:30:47.692 --> 01:30:49.820
<b><font color="#ffff00">He's waving his hammer
around and everything!</font></b>

01:31:48.628 --> 01:31:50.130
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ah!</font></b>

01:32:08.189 --> 01:32:09.691
<b><font color="#ffff00">Confirming ship is hostile.</font></b>

01:32:09.858 --> 01:32:11.735
<b><font color="#ffff00">Confirmed, ship is hostile.</font></b>

01:32:11.818 --> 01:32:13.240
<b><font color="#ffff00">You have permission to engage.</font></b>

01:32:13.319 --> 01:32:14.536
<b><font color="#ffff00">Roger.</font></b>

01:32:14.612 --> 01:32:15.738
<b><font color="#ffff00">Missiles locked.</font></b>

01:32:16.573 --> 01:32:18.325
<b><font color="#ffff00">Missiles away.</font></b>

01:32:19.784 --> 01:32:20.956
<b><font color="#ffff00">Missiles off target.</font></b>

01:32:21.036 --> 01:32:23.755
<b><font color="#ffff00">I repeat, target missed.
I'm losing control.</font></b>

01:32:23.830 --> 01:32:26.629
<b><font color="#ffff00">Mayday! Mayday!
Lost positive control.</font></b>

01:32:28.752 --> 01:32:29.753
<b><font color="#ffff00">What are you doing?</font></b>

01:32:29.836 --> 01:32:31.338
<b><font color="#ffff00">My signal's not connecting.</font></b>

01:32:33.631 --> 01:32:34.632
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane!</font></b>

01:32:34.716 --> 01:32:35.808
<b><font color="#ffff00">Come on.</font></b>

01:33:18.093 --> 01:33:19.390
<b><font color="#ffff00">Are you all right?</font></b>

01:33:19.552 --> 01:33:20.553
<b><font color="#ffff00">You saved my life.</font></b>

01:33:24.182 --> 01:33:25.183
<b><font color="#ffff00">Yeah.</font></b>

01:33:25.266 --> 01:33:26.563
<b><font color="#ffff00">I guess I did.</font></b>

01:33:34.359 --> 01:33:35.360
<b><font color="#ffff00">Mmm.</font></b>

01:33:35.735 --> 01:33:36.736
<b><font color="#ffff00">Darcy?</font></b>

01:33:37.070 --> 01:33:38.071
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane!</font></b>

01:33:38.154 --> 01:33:40.498
<b><font color="#ffff00">- Ian!
- Selvig!</font></b>

01:33:41.032 --> 01:33:42.204
<b><font color="#ffff00">Mew mew!</font></b>

01:33:45.829 --> 01:33:47.706
<b><font color="#ffff00">Mind the gap.</font></b>

01:33:49.958 --> 01:33:50.998
<b><font color="#ffff00">How do I get to Greenwich?</font></b>

01:33:52.043 --> 01:33:54.045
<b><font color="#ffff00">Take this train.
Three stops.</font></b>

01:33:56.131 --> 01:33:58.634
<b><font color="#ffff00">Mind the gap.</font></b>

01:34:00.552 --> 01:34:02.520
<b><font color="#ffff00">Sorry. Sorry.</font></b>

01:34:40.008 --> 01:34:41.681
<b><font color="#ffff00">- We're out of time.
- Jane.</font></b>

01:34:42.802 --> 01:34:43.928
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane!</font></b>

01:35:09.871 --> 01:35:11.293
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thor!</font></b>

01:35:12.290 --> 01:35:13.337
<b><font color="#ffff00">We're too late.</font></b>

01:35:14.709 --> 01:35:16.803
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Convergence is at its peak.</font></b>

01:35:17.670 --> 01:35:18.796
<b><font color="#ffff00">Can those things stop him?</font></b>

01:35:18.922 --> 01:35:20.014
<b><font color="#ffff00">Not from here.</font></b>

01:35:20.173 --> 01:35:22.972
<b><font color="#ffff00">We can't get close enough.</font></b>

01:35:24.010 --> 01:35:25.262
<b><font color="#ffff00">Loan.</font></b>

01:35:50.578 --> 01:35:51.579
<b><font color="#ffff00">Malekith!</font></b>

01:35:58.962 --> 01:36:02.216
<b><font color="#ffff00">Darkness returns, Asgardian.</font></b>

01:36:02.340 --> 01:36:05.640
<b><font color="#ffff00">Have you come to witness
the end of your universe?</font></b>

01:36:05.718 --> 01:36:07.766
<b><font color="#ffff00">I've come to accept your surrender.</font></b>

01:36:27.323 --> 01:36:29.417
<b><font color="#ffff00">You think you can stop this?</font></b>

01:36:30.118 --> 01:36:32.917
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Aether cannot be destroyed.</font></b>

01:36:33.037 --> 01:36:34.710
<b><font color="#ffff00">But you can.</font></b>

01:37:20.251 --> 01:37:22.253
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thor! No.</font></b>

01:37:32.597 --> 01:37:33.644
<b><font color="#ffff00">Jane!</font></b>

01:37:55.203 --> 01:37:56.204
<b><font color="#ffff00">Ah!</font></b>

01:38:04.337 --> 01:38:05.930
<b><font color="#ffff00">Everybody okay?</font></b>

01:38:50.508 --> 01:38:52.431
<b><font color="#ffff00">He's gonna come back.</font></b>

01:38:54.929 --> 01:38:56.806
<b><font color="#ffff00">Except, you know,</font></b>

01:38:56.931 --> 01:38:59.104
<b><font color="#ffff00">last time he was gone for,
like, two years.</font></b>

01:38:59.183 --> 01:39:01.106
<b><font color="#ffff00">Well, it's only been two days, so...</font></b>

01:39:03.020 --> 01:39:04.863
<b><font color="#ffff00">Did he say anything before he left?</font></b>

01:39:04.981 --> 01:39:07.154
<b><font color="#ffff00">Yeah, he had to figure some
stuff out with his father.</font></b>

01:39:07.233 --> 01:39:11.363
<b><font color="#ffff00">He kinda committed treason...
On our way out.</font></b>

01:39:16.200 --> 01:39:17.247
<b><font color="#ffff00">Oh.</font></b>

01:39:19.871 --> 01:39:24.547
<b><font color="#ffff00">You once said there would
never be a wiser king than me.</font></b>

01:39:24.709 --> 01:39:25.710
<b><font color="#ffff00">You were wrong.</font></b>

01:39:26.294 --> 01:39:30.174
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Alignment has brought
all the realms together.</font></b>

01:39:30.256 --> 01:39:33.385
<b><font color="#ffff00">Every one of them saw you
offer your life to save them.</font></b>

01:39:34.051 --> 01:39:38.477
<b><font color="#ffff00">What can Asgard offer
its new king in return?</font></b>

01:39:39.640 --> 01:39:41.517
<b><font color="#ffff00">My life.</font></b>

01:39:42.643 --> 01:39:45.362
<b><font color="#ffff00">Father, I cannot be king of Asgard.</font></b>

01:39:45.438 --> 01:39:50.239
<b><font color="#ffff00">I will protect Asgard and all the
realms with my last and every breath,</font></b>

01:39:50.359 --> 01:39:52.612
<b><font color="#ffff00">but I cannot do so from that chair.</font></b>

01:39:52.737 --> 01:39:56.867
<b><font color="#ffff00">Loki, for all his grave imbalance,
understood rule as I know I never will.</font></b>

01:39:57.867 --> 01:40:00.541
<b><font color="#ffff00">The brutality, the sacrifice...</font></b>

01:40:00.703 --> 01:40:02.171
<b><font color="#ffff00">it changes you.</font></b>

01:40:02.246 --> 01:40:05.671
<b><font color="#ffff00">I'd rather be a good man
than a great king.</font></b>

01:40:06.250 --> 01:40:11.051
<b><font color="#ffff00">Is this my son I hear,
or the woman he loves?</font></b>

01:40:11.130 --> 01:40:13.679
<b><font color="#ffff00">When you speak,
do I never hear Mother's voice?</font></b>

01:40:15.676 --> 01:40:18.225
<b><font color="#ffff00">This is not for Jane, Father.</font></b>

01:40:18.304 --> 01:40:20.727
<b><font color="#ffff00">She does not know
what I came here to say.</font></b>

01:40:20.806 --> 01:40:24.151
<b><font color="#ffff00">Now, forbid me to see her,
or say she can rule at my side.</font></b>

01:40:24.268 --> 01:40:25.611
<b><font color="#ffff00">It changes nothing.</font></b>

01:40:26.187 --> 01:40:29.532
<b><font color="#ffff00">One son who wanted
the throne too much,</font></b>

01:40:30.441 --> 01:40:32.569
<b><font color="#ffff00">another who will not take it.</font></b>

01:40:33.110 --> 01:40:34.862
<b><font color="#ffff00">Is this my legacy?</font></b>

01:40:35.029 --> 01:40:36.622
<b><font color="#ffff00">Loki died with honor.</font></b>

01:40:37.573 --> 01:40:38.950
<b><font color="#ffff00">I shall try to live the same.</font></b>

01:40:39.033 --> 01:40:40.455
<b><font color="#ffff00">Is that not legacy enough?</font></b>

01:40:51.462 --> 01:40:53.806
<b><font color="#ffff00">It belongs to you.</font></b>

01:40:54.549 --> 01:40:56.301
<b><font color="#ffff00">If you are worthy of it.</font></b>

01:40:56.384 --> 01:40:58.887
<b><font color="#ffff00">I shall try to be.</font></b>

01:41:00.304 --> 01:41:05.026
<b><font color="#ffff00">I cannot give you my blessing,
nor can I wish you good fortune.</font></b>

01:41:05.977 --> 01:41:07.650
<b><font color="#ffff00">I know.</font></b>

01:41:10.481 --> 01:41:13.826
<b><font color="#ffff00">If I were proud of the man
my son had become,</font></b>

01:41:14.318 --> 01:41:16.662
<b><font color="#ffff00">even that, I could not say.</font></b>

01:41:19.156 --> 01:41:22.786
<b><font color="#ffff00">It would speak only from my heart.</font></b>

01:41:24.161 --> 01:41:25.583
<b><font color="#ffff00">Go.</font></b>

01:41:26.664 --> 01:41:28.166
<b><font color="#ffff00">My son.</font></b>

01:41:30.293 --> 01:41:31.545
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thank you, Father.</font></b>

01:41:47.143 --> 01:41:48.190
<b><font color="#ffff00">No.</font></b>

01:41:49.520 --> 01:41:51.193
<b><font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font></b>

01:44:09.201 --> 01:44:11.624
<b><font color="#ffff00">I present to you,</font></b>

01:44:12.329 --> 01:44:15.833
<b><font color="#ffff00">Taneleer Tivan, the Collector.</font></b>

01:44:17.334 --> 01:44:18.506
<b><font color="#ffff00">Whoa...</font></b>

01:44:21.589 --> 01:44:26.140
<b><font color="#ffff00">Asgardians, it's an honor.</font></b>

01:44:29.847 --> 01:44:31.941
<b><font color="#ffff00">You know why we're here.</font></b>

01:44:35.644 --> 01:44:37.567
<b><font color="#ffff00">Of course.</font></b>

01:44:38.397 --> 01:44:40.650
<b><font color="#ffff00">But, if I may ask,</font></b>

01:44:40.816 --> 01:44:44.696
<b><font color="#ffff00">why not keep it secure
in your own vault?</font></b>

01:44:44.820 --> 01:44:47.744
<b><font color="#ffff00">The Tesseract is
already on Asgard.</font></b>

01:44:47.865 --> 01:44:51.415
<b><font color="#ffff00">It is not wise to keep two
Infinity Stones so close together.</font></b>

01:44:52.036 --> 01:44:54.539
<b><font color="#ffff00">That's very wise.</font></b>

01:45:04.381 --> 01:45:05.758
<b><font color="#ffff00">I can assure you,</font></b>

01:45:07.009 --> 01:45:12.231
<b><font color="#ffff00">it will be absolutely safe here,</font></b>

01:45:14.433 --> 01:45:16.936
<b><font color="#ffff00">in my collection.</font></b>

01:45:18.103 --> 01:45:20.526
<b><font color="#ffff00">See that it is.</font></b>

01:45:39.083 --> 01:45:41.586
<b><font color="#ffff00">One down.</font></b>

01:45:43.087 --> 01:45:45.590
<b><font color="#ffff00">Five to go.</font></b>